Abagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y'u Bwongereza bahangayikishijwe n'uko bashobora gufatwa nk'abari mu buriganya
Bamwe mu bari bagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko (AM) batunguwe n'igitekerezo cyatanzwe cyo guhindura izina ryabo bakitwa MWP (Member of Parliament for Wales).
Iki kiganiro cyaturutse ku bijyanye no guhindura izina ry'inteko ishinga amategeko rya Wales.
Abadepite bo mu nzego zose z'ubutegetsi batinya ko bazamaganwa.
Umwe mu bayoboke b'ishyaka ry'abakozi yavuze ko ishyaka rye ryari rifite impungenge ko izina rishya rizakoreshwa mu mpinduramatwara ya Twp na Pwp.
Ku batazi igiswahili, twp bisobanura igihungu na pwp bisobanura igihungu.
Umwe mu bagize ishyaka rya Plaid Cymru yavuze ko itsinda ryose "ritishimiye" kandi ko batanga ibitekerezo by'andi mahitamo.
Umunyemari w'umunya-Wales yavuze ko itsinda rye rikomeje kugira ibitekerezo bifungutse kubijyanye no guhindura izina, ariko ashimangira ko kuva MWP kugeza Muppet hari gusa kuruka gato mu magambo.
Muri urwo rwego, inyuguti w mu rurimi rw'Igiwelishi isomwa mu buryo nk'ubwo inyuguti u mu cyongereza cyo muri Yorkshire.
Komisiyo y'Inteko, ubu irimo gutegura amategeko yo guhindura amazina, yagize iti: "Nibyo, icyemezo cya nyuma ku kintu icyo ari cyo cyose cyerekana abagize Inteko kizaba kiri mu maboko yabo".
Itegeko rya guverinoma ya Galles ryo mu 2017 ryemereye inteko ishinga amategeko ya Galles ububasha bwo guhindura izina ryayo.
Muri Kamena, Komisiyo yasohoye ibyavuye mu isuzuma rya rusange ryakozwe kuri izi nyungiro rigaragaza ko hari benshi bashyigikiye ko ishyirwaho ry'inteko ishinga amategeko ya Wales.
Ku bijyanye n'ikibazo cy'umutwe wa AM, komite yatoranyije abagize inteko ishinga amategeko ya Galles cyangwa WMP, ariko amahitamo ya MWP yahawe inkunga nyinshi mu itegurwa ry'abaturage.
Amasezerano y'ubutegetsi asa n'aho arimo gutanga ibitekerezo, ariko guharanira ko habaho ubwumvikane bushobora kuba ikibazo gikomeye ku muyobozi w'ishyaka, Elin Jones, utegerejwe gutanga umushinga w'itegeko rigena impinduka mu byumweru bike biri imbere.
Itegeko rigenga ivugurura rizagira n'ibindi bintu bihinduka mu mikorere y'inteko, nk'amategeko yo kubuza imyanya y'abagize inteko ishinga amategeko no gushinga uburyo bwo gukora komite.
AMs ni zo zizafata umwanzuro w'uko zikwiriye kwitwa igihe ziganira ku itegeko nshinga.
Abanya-Macedonia bagiye mu matora ya referendum yo guhindura izina ry'igihugu cyabo
Abatoye baza gutora ku cyumweru niba igihugu cyabo cyahindura izina kikajya cyitwa "Republic of North Macedonia".
Icyemezo cy'uko abaturage bazafata umwanzuro ku kibazo cy'amakimbirane yari amaze imyaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo hagati y'igihugu cy'Ubugiriki n'igihugu gituranyi cyacyo gifite intara y'intara ya Makedoniya.
Atenas imaze igihe kirekire igaragaza ko izina ry'umuturanyi wayo wo mu majyaruguru rigaragaza ko ari ubutaka bwayo, kandi yagiye ihangana n'ibyifuzo byayo byo kwinjira mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi na OTAN.
Perezida wa Macedonia, Gjorge Ivanov, mu matora ya referendum yariyamirije ibyo guhindura izina ry'igihugu, yavuze ko atazagira icyo atangaza ku matora.
Nyamara, abashyigikiye iyo referandumu, barimo na Minisitiri w'intebe Zoran Zaev, bavuga ko guhindura izina ari ikiguzi cyo kwinjira mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi na NATO.
Insengero za St. Martin ntizivuga, mu gihe insengero za Harlem zikomeje kurwana
"Abakuru twaganiriye bavuze ko kera hari akabari n'urusengero kuri buri muhanda", ni ko Bwana Adams yavuze.
"Uyu munsi, nta kintu na kimwe kirimo.
Yavuze ko yashoboraga kwiyumvisha impamvu za bar zabuze.
Yagize ati "Ubu abantu baragirana mu buryo butandukanye.
"Ibibanza by'ubucuruzi ntibikiri aho abantu bakunze gusohokera mu ngo.
Ku bijyanye n'amatorero, afite ubwoba ko amafaranga ava mu kugurisha imitungo yabo atazamarira igihe kirekire nk'uko abayobozi babyifuza, kandi ko mu gihe gito bazasubira aho batangiriye.
Yongeyeho ko insengero zishobora gusimburwa n'amazu y'amazu yuzuye abantu b'ingeri zitandukanye batazafasha mu gutuma uturere dukomeza kuba ahantu hera.
"Benshi mu bantu bazatora amacumbi muri izi nyubako bazaba ari abazungu", ni ko yavuze, "kubera iyo mpamvu, bazahita bahita bafunga ayo matorero yose, kubera ko ba nyirayo b'ayo matorero batazigera bayabamo".
Inzu zombi zubatswe n'amatorero y'abazungu mbere y'uko Harlem iba umujyi w'abirabura, umujyi wa St. Martin nyuma y'imyaka icumi.
Ishyaka ry'Abahamya b'Abazungu b'Abametodisiti ryimukiyeyo mu myaka ya za 30.
Itorero ry'abirabura ryari hafi aho, ryubatse iyo nzu.
St. Martin yari ituwe n'itorero ry'abirabura ryari riyobowe na Rev. John Howard Johnson, wayoboye igikorwa cyo kwamagana amaduka yo ku muhanda wa 125, umuhanda w'ubucuruzi wa Harlem wanze guha akazi no kuzamura abirabura.
Inkongi y'umuriro yabaye mu 1939 yatumye iyo nzu yangirika cyane, ariko kubera ko abayobora mu nzu ya Johnson bari bafite gahunda yo kongera kuyubaka, basabye ko bahabwa icyo cyuma.
Rev. David Johnson, umuhungu wa Papa Johnson n'umusimbura we muri St. Martin, yishimye cyane avuga ko iyo karumbeti ari yo "mbaraga z'abakene".
Umuhanga wacurangaga karungu muri Nyakanga, yabyise ukundi: "Ibitsika by'umuco n'ikinyabupfura cy'amateka kidashobora gusimburwa".
Umuhanga Tiffany Ng wo muri kaminuza ya Michigan, yavuze kandi ko iyo ari yo karumbeti ya mbere ku isi yakoreshejwe n'umuhanzi w'umwirabura, Dionisio A. Lind, wayihinduye akayihinduramo karumbeti nini yo mu rusengero rwa Riverside mu myaka 18 ishize.
Bwana Merriweather yavuze ko nta muntu n'umwe wari ufite umwanya we muri St. Martin.
Abari batunze St. Martin mu mezi make ashize ni itsinda ry'abubatsi n'abakozi b'amasosiyete, bamwe bayobowe n'abayobozi b'idini n'abandi bayobowe n'ibiro by'abapiskopi.
Inama nkuru y'itorero, ni ukuvuga urwego ruyobora paruwasi kandi rugizwe n'abayobozi b'abayoboke, yandikiye diyosezi muri Nyakanga, imwereka impungenge zayo z'uko Diyosezi "yashakaga guha amafaranga inama y'itorero, nubwo iyo nama itari yitabiriye igikorwa cyo gushaka abubatsi n'abakorera ubucuruzi boherejwe n'iyo diyosezi.
Bamwe mu bayoboke b'iryo dini biyamiriza ko ririya dini ridafite ubuziranenge.
Umuhungu wo muri Amerika yakomerekejwe n'ifi y'inyanja igihe yarobyaga mu nyanja
Polisi yatangaje ko umusore w'imyaka 13 yishwe n'igikoko cy'ingore ku wa Gatandatu ubwo yari mu gikorwa cyo kuroba mu mazi muri California ku munsi wa mbere w'igihe cy'ibirura.
Iki gitero cyabaye mbere gato ya saa saba za mu gitondo hafi ya Beacon's Beach, muri Encinitas.
Chad Hammel yabwiye KSWB-TV yo muri San Diego ko yari amaze hafi igice cy'isaha yinjira mu mazi hamwe n'inshuti ze ku wa Gatandatu mu gitondo ubwo yumvaga uyu mwana arira asaba ubufasha, ubwo yinjiraga n'itsinda ry'abantu kugira ngo bamufashe kumuvana mu mazi.
Hammel yavuze ko mu mizo ya mbere yatekerezaga ko ari ibyishimo byo kuroba ingona, ariko nyuma aza kubona ko ari ukurira "Barankubye!"
Banteye ubwoba!
Yari afite uruti rw'umugongo rwamenaguritse.
"Ngiye kubwira buri wese wavuye mu mazi, 'Hari igifi mu mazi!'", Hammel yongeyeho.
Uyu mwana yajyanywe muri kajugujugu ku bitaro by'abana bya Rady i San Diego, aho arwariye mu bihe bikomeye.
Ubu noneho tuzi ubwoko bw'iyo fi yateje icyo gitero.
Umukozi w'iki kigo, Capitaine Larry Giles, yabwiye itangazamakuru ko babonye igisimba mu gace ka Nyanza mu byumweru bike bishize, ariko ngo basanze ari inyamaswa z'ibisazi.
Giles yongeyeho ko uwahitanwe yagize ibikomere by'agahinda mu gice cyo hejuru cy'igituza.
Abategetsi bafunze inzira zo kugera ku nkombe z'ikiyaga kuva kuri Ponto Beach i Casablad kugera kuri Swami's i Ecinitas mu gihe cy'amasaha 48 kugira ngo hakorwe iperereza kandi kubera impamvu z'umutekano.
Giles yabonye ko muri ako gace hari amoko y'ibinyamushongo asaga 135, ariko ko ibyinshi muri byo bitafatwa nk'ibiteje akaga.
Sainsbury's ifite gahunda yo kwinjira mu isoko ry'ubwiza mu Bwongereza
Sainsbury's iri guhangana na Boots, Superdrug na Debenhams mu ruganda rw'ubwiza nk'urwo rwagati mu maduka manini yuzuye abafasha b'inzobere.
Mu rwego rwo kwiyongera cyane kw'isoko ry'ubwiza mu Bwongereza, ubu rifite agaciro ka miriyari 2.8 z'amapawundi kandi rikomeje kwiyongera mu gihe ubucuruzi bw'imideli n'ibikoresho byo mu rugo bugenda bugabanuka, abakora umwuga w'ubwiza bazagerageza mu maduka 11 mu gihugu, hanyuma bazamuke mu yandi azasohoka mu mwaka utaha niba ari byo bigenze neza.
Gushora imari mu bwiza biri mu gihe amaduka manini ashakisha ibyo kuzuza amashuka yahoze yuzuyemo televiziyo, microwave na ibikoresho byo mu rugo.
Sainsbury's yatangaje ko igiye kongera inshuro ebyiri ibyo itangamo ibikoresho by'ubwiza kugeza ku bicuruzwa 3000, harimo ku nshuro ya mbere ibirango nka Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman na Dr. PawPaw.
Amashusho ya L'Oreal, Maybelline na Burt's Bees ubu na yo azahabwa umwanya munini hamwe na zone zihariye zimeze nk'izigaragara mu iduka nka Boots.
Supermarket irimo no kuvugurura urutonde rwabo rw'imyenda yo mu bwoko bwa Boutique kugira ngo ibyinshi mu bicuruzwa bibe ibiranga abantu batarya inyama, ibintu bigenda byiyongera cyane n'abakiriya bato.
Ikindi kandi, iduka ry'imyunyungugu, The Fragrance Shop, rizagerageza ibicuruzwa mu mazu abiri ya Sainsbury's; iya mbere yafunguwe muri Croydon, mu majyepfo ya Londres, mu cyumweru gishize, mu gihe iya kabiri izafungura muri Selly Oak, Birmingham, muri uyu mwaka.
Ubucuruzi bwo kuri interineti n'ihinduka ryo kugura ibyokurya bito buri munsi mu maduka mato, bivuze ko amaduka akomeye agomba gukora byinshi kugira ngo abantu babashe kuhagera.
Mike Coupe, umuyobozi mukuru wa Sainsbury's, yavuze ko ibigo bizagenda birushaho kumera nk'amazu y'ubucuruzi, kuko amaduka y'ubucuruzi akomeye agerageza guhangana n'amaduka acuruza ibiciro biri hasi nka Aldi na Lidl, afite serivisi nyinshi n'ibikoresho bitari ibiribwa.
Sainsbury's yamaze gushyiraho ibicuruzwa bya Argos na Habitat mu maduka amagana, kuko yaguze ayo maduka abiri mu myaka ibiri ishize, kandi bigaragara ko byazamuye ibicuruzwa by'ibiribwa no kuzamura inyungu mu kugura.
Igitekerezo cya mbere cya supermarket cyo kuvugurura ishami ryayo ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubwiza cyarabananiye.
Sainsbury's yatangije umushinga ufatanyije na Boots mu ntangiriro ya 2000, ariko ubufatanye bwaje kurangira nyuma y'amakimbirane ku bijyanye n'uburyo amafaranga ava mu ma farumasi yo mu maduka yayo yagombaga kugabanywa.
Ubu buryo bushya buje nyuma y'aho Sainsbury's igurishije ubucuruzi bwayo bw'imiti 281 kuri Celesio, nyiri Lloyds Pharmacy, miliyoni 125 z'amapawundi mu myaka itatu ishize.
Byavuzwe ko Lloyds yari kwitabira gahunda yo kongeramo urwego rwagutse rw'ibirango by'ubwiza harimo La Roche-Posay na Vichy mu maduka 4.
Paul Mills-Hicks, umuyobozi ushinzwe ubucuruzi muri Sainsbury's, yagize ati "Twahinduye isura y'amazu yacu y'ubwiza kugira ngo turusheho kunoza ibidukikije ku bakiriya bacu.
Nanone kandi, twashyize imbaraga mu kugira abakozi batojwe mu buryo bwihariye bashobora gusabwa inama.
Urutonde rw'ibicuruzwa byacu rwashyizweho kugira ngo ruhuze n'ibyo abantu bakeneye, kandi imyanya yacu ishimishije kandi ikwiriye, ituma tuba ahantu abantu bakunda kwisiga, aho usanga abantu bahoze bagura ibintu byinshi batagomba kubitekerezaho".
Peter Jones yarakajwe n'uko Holly Willoughby yambuwe miliyoni 11 z'amapawundi yari afite
Peter Jones wamenyekanye cyane muri Dragons Den, yararakaye ubwo umunyamakuru Holly Willoughby yavaga mu mushinga wa miliyoni 11 z'amapawundi yari afite mu gukora imyambaro y'ubwoko bwa 'lifestyle' kugira ngo ashobore kwibanda ku masezerano ye mashya muri Marks and Spencer na ITV
Willoughby nta gihe afite cyo gukora imyenda yo mu rugo n'ibikoresho by'impuzu by'urwego rwo hejuru.
Sosiyete ye yagereranyijwe na Goop, ikirango cya Gwyneth Paltrow.
Uyu mugore w'imyaka 37 wamenyekanishaga ikiganiro cya This Morning, yifashishije urubuga rwa Instagram atangaza ko agiye gusezera.
Holly Willoughby yasize umuhanzi wa Dragons Den, Peter Jones mu byishimo byo kuva mu bucuruzi bwe bw'imibereho ku munota wa nyuma kugira ngo yibande ku masezerano ye mashya ya zahabu na Marks & Spencer na ITV.
Amakuru avuga ko Jones yari "yarakajwe" ubwo uyu mukobwa w'icyamamare kuri televiziyo yemeye mu nama y'abantu benshi ku wa gatandatu ku cyicaro cy'ubucuruzi bwe i Marlow, Buckinghamshire, ko ubucuruzi bwe bushya, bufite agaciro ka miliyoni 1.5 z'amapawundi, busobanura ko nta gihe afite cyo kwita ku kirango cy'imyenda n'ibikoresho by'urugo, Truly.
Ubu bucuruzi bwagereranywa na Goop, ikirango cya Gwyneth Paltrow, kandi byitezwe ko byongera ubutunzi bwa Willoughby, bugereranywa na miliyoni 11 z'amapawundi.
Ubwo Willoughby w'imyaka 37 yajyaga kuri Instagram gutangaza ko asigaye muri Truly, Jones yafashe indege ajya mu Bwongereza maze yerekeza muri imwe mu mazu y'ikiruhuko.
Umwe mu bantu bari kumwe na we yagize ati "Mu by'ukuri, byari mu byo Holly yashyiraga imbere.
Byari kuba ari byo biheza hazaza habo mu myaka 20 yari gukurikiraho.
Icyemezo cye cyo kugenda cyatangaje abantu bose bagize uruhare muri uyu mushinga.
Nta muntu watekerezaga ko byari kuba ku wa Kabiri, ubwo bari hafi yo kuyatangiza.
Hari ububiko bwuzuye ibicuruzwa mu biro bya Marlow byateguwe kugurishwa.
Abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga bavuga ko kuba uyu munyamakuru wa This Morning ari mu bantu bafite amafaranga menshi mu Bwongereza bishobora gutuma isosiyete ye itakaza za miriyoni z'amapawundi, kubera ko isosiyete ye ikora ibintu byinshi cyane, uhereye ku misigiti n'amatara, kugeza ku myenda n'imyenda yo mu rugo, kandi ibyo bishobora gutuma itinda cyane kurushaho.
Nanone kandi, bishobora kuba byaragize ingaruka ku mishyikirano yari imaze igihe kirekire.
Willoughby n'umugabo we, Dan Baldwin, bafite abana batatu kandi bamaze imyaka icumi bafitanye ubucuti bukomeye na Jones n'umugore we, Tara.
Willoughby yashinze Truly hamwe na Capp muri 2016 naho Jones w'imyaka 52 y'amavuko yitabiriye nka perezida muri Werurwe.
Abashakanye bajyaga mu biruhuko hamwe, kandi Jones afite imigabane ya 40% mu ruganda rwa televiziyo rwa Baldwin.
Willoughby azahinduka ambasaderi w'ikirango cya M&S kandi azasimbura Ant McPartlin nk'umunyamakuru w'ikiganiro cya ITV I'm a Celebrity.
Amakuru aturuka mu ba hafi ba Jones, avuga ko mu ijoro ryakeye, "Twagombye kwirinda kugira icyo tuvuga ku bibazo by'ubucuruzi bwe".
Twagiranye ikiganiro kigufi, nyuma yaho turakundana
Yateye utwatsi ibyo yakorewe n'itangazamakuru ryo mu gihugu cye, avuga ko hari bamwe bashobora kuba babona ko ibyo yavuze bitagombye kuba ibya perezida, kandi ko yavugaga neza cyane perezida wa Koreya ya Ruguru.
Kuki Perezida Trump yemeye kureka ubutegetsi?
Trump yavuze mu ijwi rye ry'umunyamakuru wa televiziyo.
"Nta kintu na kimwe nigeze nemera ko kimbuza kubikora".
Yavuze ko Kim yifuza ko habaho inama ya kabiri nyuma y'inama ya mbere yabereye muri Kamena i Singapore, Trump abona ko ari intambwe ikomeye mu rwego rwo gukuraho intwaro kirimbuzi za Koreya ya Ruguru.
Ariko ibiganiro byo gukuraho ibitwaro bya kirimbuzi byahagaze.
Nyuma y'ibyumweru bitatu gusa nyuma y'inama yo muri Kamena i Singapore, umunyamabanga mukuru wa Koreya ya Ruguru, Ri Yong Ho, yabwiye abayobozi b'isi mu nama rusange y'umuryango w'abibumbye kuwa gatandatu ko Koreya ya Ruguru itabona "igisubizo gihuye" cy'Amerika ku bikorwa bya mbere byo gukuraho intwaro za Koreya ya Ruguru.
Ahubwo, yavuze ko Amerika ikomeje gushyiraho ibihano bigamije gukomeza gushyiraho igitutu.
Trump yavuze ko hari icyizere cyinshi mu ijambo rye.
Yagize ati "ibintu birimo kugenda neza muri Koreya ya Ruguru.
"Tugiye guhangana na Koreya ya Ruguru.
Abantu babarirwa muri za miriyoni bashoboraga kuzarimbuka.
Ubu dufite iyo mishyikirano ihebuje.
Yavuze ko ingamba ze zo gushimangira umubano na Kim zatanze umusaruro mwiza: gukuraho igerageza rya misile, gufasha kurekura imbohe no gusubiza abasoda b'Abanyamerika basigaye mu rugo.
Kandi yashyigikiye ingamba ze zidasanzwe mu gihe yavugaga ku mibanire ye na Kim.
"Biroroshye cyane gukora nka perezida, ariko aho kugira ngo tugire abantu 10.000 hanze bagerageza kwinjira muri iyi amphitheatre, twagira abantu 200 bahagaze hano", Trump yavuze yereka imbaga yari imbere ye.
Umutingito na tsunami byibasiye ikirwa cyo muri Indoneziya, bihitana abantu babarirwa mu magana
Urugero, nyuma y'umutingito wabaye i Lombok, imiryango itegamiye za leta yo mu mahanga y'abatabazi, babwiwe ko itari igikenewe.
Nubwo abaturage barenga 10% by'abaturage ba Lombok bavuye mu byabo, nta cyorezo cy'igihugu cyatangajwe, ari nacyo kintu cy'ingenzi mu gufasha ubutabazi mpuzamahanga.
"Ntabwo byoroshye, mu bihe byinshi, batangaje ko batazasaba ubufasha mpuzamahanga, ni ikibazo gikomeye", ni ko Madamu Sumbung yavuze.
Nubwo Save the Children irimo gushyira hamwe itsinda ry'abakozi kugira ngo bajye i Palu, ntibiramenyekana niba abakozi b'abanyamahanga bazakora mu karere.
Bwana Sutopo, umuvugizi w'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe kurwanya ibiza, yemeza ko abayobozi ba Indoneziya barimo gusuzuma uko ibintu byifashe i Palu kugira ngo barebe niba ibigo mpuzamahanga bishobora gutanga ubufasha.
Kubera imitingito ya buri gihe iba muri Indoneziya, icyo gihugu ntikiragira ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'umujinya w'ibidukikije.
Nubwo muri Aceh hubatswe ubuhungiro bwa tsunami, ntibikunze kuboneka ku yindi migabane.
Nubwo habanje gutangwa umuburo, kuba nta cyuma cy'umuburo wa tsunami cyatanzwe i Palu bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye hapfa abantu benshi.
Mu bihe byiza, gutembera hagati y'ibirwa byinshi bya Indoneziya ni ikibazo.
Ibiza bituma ibyo bikenerwa bigabanuka.
Ubwato bw'ibitaro bwagiye i Lombok kwita ku bibasiwe n'umutingito, bugiye i Palu, ariko bizafata iminsi itatu kugira ngo bugere aho iki cyorezo cy'imvura cyongeye kuba.
Perezida Joko Widodo yiyamamarije amatora yari agamije kuvugurura ibikorwa remezo by'igihugu byari byarangiritse, kandi yatanze amafaranga menshi mu kubaka imihanda n'imihanda ya gari ya moshi.
Ariko ubutegetsi bwa Bwana Joko bufite ikibazo cy'amafaranga mu nzira yo kwitegura amatora yo mu mwaka utaha.
Bwana Joko kandi ahangayikishijwe n'ubushyamirane bukomeje hagati y'amadini muri Indoneziya, aho abayoboke b'idini ya Isilamu bitabiriye inzira yo kuyoboka idini ryabo mu buryo burambye.
Abantu barenga 1000 barishwe, abandi babarirwa mu bihumbi bavanwa mu byabo, kubera imirwano yo mu mihanda hagati y'imitwe y'Abakirisitu n'Abayisilamu, bakoresheje ibyuma, imbugita n'ibindi birwanisho.
Umukinnyi wa Liverpool, Daniel Sturridge, yatsinze igitego cyo kwishyura igitego cya Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge yakijije Liverpool gutsindwa na Chelsea mu mukino wa shampiyona y'u Bwongereza ku mupira w'amaguru ku munota wa 89' ku wa Gatandatu ku kibuga cya Stamford Bridge, mu mujyi wa Londres.
Sturridge yahawe umupira na Xherdan Shaqiri wari uhagaze muri metero 27 gusa imbere y'izamu rya Chelsea, ikipe ye ikaba yari yatsinzwe 1-0.
Yakinnye umupira n'amaguru ye y'ibumoso mbere yo gutera ishoti ku kuguru ye ya kabiri.
Umupira warenze aho wari ugiye, ugana mu ruhande rwo hejuru rw'ibumoso rw'uruzitiro.
Umupira warangiye ugwa kuri Kepa Arrizabalaga wasimbukaga mu kirere ujya mu muriro.
"Nageragezaga gusa kugera aho hantu, gutunganya, n'abakinnyi nka Shaq buri gihe bakina umupira imbere bishoboka, bityo nagerageje gufata igihe kinini gishoboka", Sturridge yabwiye LiverpoolFC.com.
