Erdogan yakiriwe mu buryo budasobanutse i Cologne
Kuwa gatandatu tariki ya 29 Nzeri, mu nama y'abategetsi b'ibihugu bya Turukiya n'u Budage i Berlin, mu gihe cyo gufata ifunguro rya saa sita, abantu bari basetse kandi ijuru ririmo ubururu.
Ni mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'uruzinduko rwa Perezida Erdogan mu Budage, rufite intego yo gukosora umubano w'ibihugu by'ibihangange mu muryango w'ibihugu by'Abibumbye (NATO).
Baganiriye ku bibazo byinshi, harimo uburenganzira bwa muntu, ubwisanzure bw'itangazamakuru ndetse no kwinjira kwa Turukiya muri EU.
