Ntabwo twakwirengagiza ko muri iki gihe, mu bihe by'ubucuruzi ku isi hose, ko indimi zikomeje kuba ingenzi cyane ku hazaza h'igihugu, bityo ko ibyo bigomba kugaragarira mu burezi.
Mu by'ukuri, indimi zo muri iki gihe zagombye gufatwa nk'ubuhanga mpuzamahanga bwo gushyikirana.
Amashuri yigenga azakomeza gutanga ubwo bunyuranye n'ubwiza ku rubyiruko rwo muri Scotland.
Tugomba kubikora neza.
John Edwards ni umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'amashuri yigenga muri Scotland.
Lebron azakina umukino wa mbere wa Lakers ku cyumweru i San Diego
Gutegereza birarangiye ku bakinnyi bose bifuza kureba LeBron James ku nshuro ye ya mbere mu mukino wa Los Angeles Lakers.
Umutoza w'ikipe, Like Walton, yatangaje ko James azakina umukino ubanza wa mbere wa shampiyona bahura na Denver Nuggets muri San Diego.
Ariko haracyari gufatirwa umwanzuro w'iminota azajya akina.
"Bazagomba kuba ari hejuru ya 1 na hasi ya 48", Walton yavuze ku rubuga rwa Lakers.
Umunyamakuru wa Lakers, Mike Trudell, yanditse kuri Twitter ko James ashobora kuba yakinnye iminota mike.
Nyuma y'imyitozo yo mu ntangiriro z'icyumweru, babajije James ku mikino itandatu Lakers itegura mbere y'umukino.
Ati "Kuri ubu ntabwo nkeneye imikino ya mbere kugira ngo mbe niteguye".
Ibikorwa byo kwiyamamaza kwa Trump byageze muri Virginia, kuri YouTube
Perezida Donald Trump yatangiye gahunda y'ibiterane byo kwiyamamaza muri iki gicuku i Wheeling, muri West Virginia.
Ni yo ya mbere mu biterane bitanu Trump azakora mu cyumweru gitaha, birimo n'ibyigirwa mu mijyi yo hafi ye nka Tennessee na Mississippi.
Mu gihe amatora yo kwemeza Perezida Trump yateguwe kugira ngo umukandida we yuzuze umwanya uri mu rukiko rw'ikirenga, Trump arashaka gushakisha inkunga mu matora yo mu gihe cy'imyaka icumi iri imbere, kuko abarepublika bashobora gutakaza ubutegetsi mu matora yo mu kwezi kwa cumi na kumwe.
Ni ryari Trump azitabira inama muri West Virginia, kandi se ni gute wabyirebera kuri interineti?
Igiterane cya Trump i Wheeling, West Virginia, giteganyijwe kuri uyu wa Gatandatu, tariki ya 29 Nzeri 2018, saa moya za nimugoroba.
Ushobora kureba ikiganiro cya Trump muri West Virginia ukoresheje YouTube.
Trump ashobora kuba azaganira ku rubanza rwabaye mu cyumweru gishize rw'uwitwa Brett Kavanaugh, uhatanira umwanya w'umucamanza w'ikirenga, wababajwe n'ibirego by'imibonano mpuzabitsina idakwiriye, akaba ari na byo byatumye amenyesha ko amatora yo kwemeza uwo azajya asimbura muri Sena, aza kumara icyumweru cyose, mu gihe FBI ikomeje iperereza.
Ariko intego y'ibanze y'iyi myigaragambyo ni ugufasha abarepubulikani kwitegura amatora yo mu kwezi k'Ugushyingo bafite imbaraga nshya.
Niyo mpamvu iyi myigaragambyo itanu Trump azatanga mu cyumweru gitaha igamije "gutera inkunga abaterankunga n'abamushyigikiye mu gihe abarepubulikani bagerageza kurinda no kwagura ubwiganze bafite muri Sena no mu Nteko Ishinga Amategeko", nk'uko Reuters ibitangaza.
Umuvugizi w'ishyaka rya Trump, utifuza ko izina rye ryatangazwa, yabwiye Reuters ati "gukurikirana Kongere ni ingenzi cyane ku ntego ye ku buryo perezida azagendera muri leta nyinshi zishoboka mu gihe cy'amatora".
Igiterane cya nimugoroba, kizabera muri Stade Wesbanco, gishobora kuzitabirwa n'abashyigikiye uyu mukino muri Ohio na Pennsylvania ndetse n'ibitangazamakuru byo muri Pittsburgh", nkuko byatangajwe na West Virginia Metro News.
Ku wa gatandatu, bizaba ari ku nshuro ya kabiri mu kwezi kumwe, Trump asura intara ya West Virginia, iyo ntara yatsinze amatora mu 2016 ku bwiganze bw'ibice 40%.
Trump arimo kugerageza gufasha umukandida w'Umurepubulikani muri Sena ya West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, uri ku mwanya wa nyuma mu matora.
"Si ikimenyetso cyiza kuri Morrisey kuba perezida agomba kumushyigikira mu matora", ni ko Simon Haeder, umuhanga mu bya politiki muri kaminuza ya West Virginia, yabwiye Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA igaragaza imbaraga zo gukomeza guhangana no gukomeza kugira icyizere kugeza ku mikino yo ku cyumweru
Nyuma y'ibiganiro bitatu byahuje abantu, ku wa gatandatu nyuma ya saa sita, byari byarashoboye kuba ibyo Ryder Cup yari ikeneye.
Igicuma gihinduranya imbaraga ni igitekerezo cy'imikino cyateguwe rwose ariko ni cyo abakinnyi bizera by'ukuri, cyane cyane mu marushanwa nk'aya.
None se ubu watekereza ko imbaraga ziri he?
"Bari bafite amanota atandatu imbere yabo, none ubu ni bane, bityo ngira ngo twafashe ibyo nk'inkunga ntoya", Jordan Spieth yavuze ubwo yari avuye ku kazi ku mugoroba.
Birumvikana ko u Burayi bufite amanota ane imbere yabo, naho abandi cumi na babiri bakaba bari mu mikino.
Abanyamerika, Spieth yavuze, bumva ko bafite umuyaga muke wo kubashyigikira kandi byinshi byo kwishima, mubindi bintu uburyo Spieth na Justin Thomas, bakinnye hamwe umunsi wose kandi buri wese afite amanota atatu kuri ane.
Spieth yabaye intangarugero kuva ku kibuga kugeza ku kibuga kandi arimo yigisha n'urugero.
Aya majwi ye yo gutaka yarushijeho gukomera uko yagendaga asatira, akora putt ikomeye yo guhuza umukino wa kane ubwo we na Thomas bari hasi amanota abiri nyuma ya kabiri.
Ubwo yafataga umupira wa putt watumye batsinda umukino wa 15, yasakuye amagambo nk'ayo, amagambo avuga ko atekereza ko ikipe y'Amerika itararangira.
Spieth ati "Icyo ugomba gukora ni uguhoza umutima ku ruhande rwawe".
Ni cyo abakinnyi basigaye bafite.
18 imyanya yo gukina.
Abakinnyi bafite amanota menshi kurusha Spieth na Thomas mu minsi ibiri ishize ni Francesco Molinari na Tommy Fleetwood, amateka atavugwaho rumwe ya Ryder Cup.
Abari mu itsinda ry'abari mu Burayi, bari bafite amanota ane muri ane, kandi ntibashoboraga kwibeshya.
"Moliwood" ni yo kipe yonyine itakoze bogey kuwa gatandatu nimugoroba, ariko kandi yabyiyemeje mu gitondo cyo kuwa gatandatu, ku wa gatanu nimugoroba ndetse no mu byumba icyenda bya nyuma mu gitondo cyo kuwa gatanu.
Iyo nzira, n'uburyo bigaragara ko imbaraga zabo zagiye zigera mu mbaga y'abantu kandi ziva muri iyo mbaga, byemeza ko ari bo bahanganye ku cyumweru, kandi nta mukinnyi ushobora kuba ari we ukundwa cyane mu gutsinda izuba rirenze kuri Le Golf National kurusha Fleetwood cyangwa Molinari.
Ni byiza ko byombi biba icyarimwe ku mbuga zitandukanye.
Nyamara, kuvuga iby'ubwiza bw'u Burayi biracyari kare.
Bubba Watson na Webb Simpson bahise batakaza Sergio Garcia, intwari y'umunsi wa kane, ubwo yifatanyaga na Alex Noren.
Igitego kimwe na kabiri mu cyiciro cya mbere byageze ku Munya-Spanye n'Umunyasuwede mu rwobo batigeze bageraho.
Ariko ku Cyumweru nta muntu uzamufasha kuva mu rwobo.
Ibihimba by'amatsiko n'iby'amatsiko biratangaje cyane kubona hafi bitewe n'imikoranire hagati y'impande zombi, inama zitangwa, n'izitanzwe n'uburyo ushobora guhindura uburyo bwo gukoresha mu kanya gato.
Mu itsinda rimwe, u Burayi bwatsinze neza kurusha u Burayi bwose, kandi bufite umwenda ukomeye ku munsi wa nyuma. Ariko iyi mibonano y'abantu bane, yagaragaje ko Team USA ifite imbaraga zo gutsinda, ibintu bamwe, cyane cyane Stateside, bari bashidikanyaho.
U Burayi bufite umuyobozi w'ibitego 10-6 ku munsi wa nyuma w'igikombe cya Ryder.
Uburayi buzahabwa amahirwe menshi ku munsi wa nyuma w'igikombe cya Ryder Cup nyuma yo gusohoka muri fourballs na foursomes bafite 10-6 ku banyamerika.
Twese twitwaga Tommy Fleetwood na Francesco Molinari, batwaye igitego cya mbere n'intsinzi ebyiri kuri Tiger Woods wari ugiye gutsindwa, bituma batsinda amanota ane muri Le Golf National.
Ikipe y'i Burayi ya Thomas Bjorn, iri gushaka igikombe cyayo yabuze mu myaka ibiri ishize i Hazeltine, yatsinze ikipe y'Abanyamerika yari yananiwe muri fourballs yo mu gitondo, itsinda 3-1.
Amerika yagabanyije cyane mu mikino ine, ariko ntiyabashije kugabanya ayo manota.
Ikipe ya Jim Furyk yari ikeneye amanota umunani mu mikino 12 y'umunsi wa mbere kugira ngo ikomeze kwegukana igikombe.
Fleetwood ni we mukinnyi w'umwimerere w'umugabane w'u Burayi watsinze amanota ane akomeje, mu gihe we na Molinari, bakunze kwita Molliwood nyuma y'impera z'icyumweru ziteye ubwoba, ari abakinnyi babiri ba mbere batsinze amanota ane mu mikino ine ya mbere mu mateka ya Ryder Cup.
Nyuma yo gutsinda Woods na Patrick Reed muri fourballs, bakoze neza cyane gutsinda Woods wari wararetse no gutsinda umunyamerika mushya Bryson Dechambeau na 5&4 nyinshi.
Woods, wakinnye imikino ibiri kuwa gatandatu nta gahinda cyangwa icyubahiro, yagaragaje ibihe by'uburanga, ariko ubu yatsinzwe imikino 19 muri 29 mu mikino ya fourballs na foursomes na itanu yikurikiranyije.
Justin Rose wari wararuhutse mu mikino y'amakipe ane ya shampiyona, yongeye guhura na Henrik Stenson mu mikino y'amakipe ane, atsindwa na Dustin Johnson na Brooks Koepka, nimero ya mbere n'iya gatatu ku isi.
Iburengerazuba bw'Umujyi wa Paris.
Jordan Spieth n'umukinnyi Justin Thomas batsinze inshuro eshatu, bahaye Abanyamerika amanota abiri ku wa Gatandatu.
Batsinze 2&1 ku Banya-Espagne John Rahm na Ian Poulter muri fourballs maze bongera gutsinda Poulter na Rory McIlroy 4&3 muri foursomes nyuma yo gutakaza imyanya ibiri ibanza.
Ni inshuro ebyiri gusa mu mateka ya Ryder Cup aho ikipe yazamutseho amanota ane ku giti cyabo, nubwo nk'uwafashe igikombe ubu, ikipe ya Furyk ikeneye gusa gutsinda kugira ngo ikomeze.
Ariko nyuma yo kuba uwa kabiri mu minsi ibiri, igitero cyo ku cyumweru gisa n'aho kidashoboka.
Kora y'Amajyaruguru ivuga ko ntawe ukeneye intwaro z'ubwigenge mu gihe nta cyizere
Minisitiri w'ububanyi n'amahanga wa Koreya ya Ruguru yabwiye Umuryango w'Abibumbye ku wa Gatandatu ko ibihano bikomeje byatumaga Amerika itakarizwa icyizere, kandi ko igihugu cye kitari gutanga intwaro za kirimbuzi mu bihe nk'ibyo.
Ri Yong Ho yabwiye Inama Rusange ya buri mwaka ko Koreya ya Ruguru yafashe "ingamba zikomeye zo kugaragaza ubushake" umwaka ushize, zirimo guhagarika igerageza ry'ibitwaro kirimbuzi n'ibirwanisho bya misile, guhagarika ibigo bigeragamo intwaro za kirimbuzi no kwiyemeza ku ikwirakwizwa ry'intwaro kirimbuzi n'ikoranabuhanga.
"Ariko, nta gisubizo cya Amerika tubona".
"Aho nta cyizere cyaba kiri muri Amerika nta cyizere cyaba kiri mu mutekano wacu w'igihugu, kandi mu bihe nk'ibyo nta bwo hazabaho guhererekanya intwaro ku ruhande rwacu.
Mu gihe Ri yasubizaga ku birego bya Koreya ya Ruguru byamenyekanye ku bijyanye n'uko Washington yanze guhita ikuraho intwaro kirimbuzi za nikleyeri, aho Koreya ya Ruguru izahabwa ibihembo mu gihe izaba ikora, ijambo rye ryasaga nk'irifite ireme, kuko atari guhakana ukuraho intwaro kirimbuzi ku ruhande nk'uko byagenze kuri Pyongyang mu gihe cyahise.
Ri yerekezaga ku itangazo rusange ryatanzwe na Kim Jong Un na Donald Trump mu nama ya mbere yahuje Perezida wa Amerika uri ku butegetsi n'umuyobozi wa Koreya ya Ruguru yabereye muri Singapuru ku ya 12 Kamena, ubwo Kim yiyemeje "kuvanaho intwaro kirimbuzi" ku mugabane wa Koreya mu gihe Trump yemezaga umutekano wa Koreya ya Ruguru.
Koreya ya Ruguru imaze igihe yifuza ko intambara yo muri Koreya yo mu 1950-53 yarangira, ariko Amerika yavuze ko Pyongyang ibanza gushyira intwaro zayo za kirimbuzi hasi.
Washington kandi yanze gufatira ibihano bikomeye by'amahanga Koreya ya Ruguru.
"Amerika ihora isaba ko hakorwa 'ibisasu bya kirimbuzi mbere' kandi igakomeza igitutu binyuze mu bihano kugira ngo igere ku ntego yayo yo guhatira abantu gukora, ndetse inengwa 'itangazo ryo kurangiza intambara', Ri yavuze.
"Kubona ko ibihano bishobora kuduca intege ni inzozi zidashoboka, ku batatuzi.
Ariko ikibazo ni uko ibihano bikomeje gutuma turushaho kugira amakenga.
Ri ntiyigeze avuga ku igenamigambi ry'inama ya kabiri hagati ya Kim na Trump, iyo perezida wa Amerika yavuze mu muryango w'abibumbye mu ntangiriro z'icyumweru gishize.
Ariko, yavuze ku nama eshatu hagati ya Kim na Perezida wa Koreya y'Epfo, Moon Jae-in, mu mezi atanu ashize, yongeraho ati: "Iyo ikindi gice cy'iyi ngingo yo gukuraho intwaro kirimbuzi cyaba Koreya y'Epfo aho kuba Amerika, gukuraho intwaro kirimbuzi bya Koreya y'Epfo ntibyari kugera mu gihirahiro.
Nyamara, imvugo ya Ri mu ijambo rye itandukanye cyane n'iy'umwaka ushize ubwo yabwiraga Inama Rusange y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ko ibitero by'ibitwaro bya kirimbuzi bya Koreya ya Ruguru ku gihugu cya Amerika byanze bikunze bizakorwa nyuma y'aho Perezida mubi Trump yise Kim Jong-un ikiremwa cya kirimbuzi cy'ubwiyahuzi.
Muri uyu mwaka muri ONU, Trump, umwaka ushize wari warahaye ubwoba Koreya ya Ruguru ko izarimburwa burundu, yashimiye Kim kubera ubutwari bwe mu gufata ingamba zo gukuraho intwaro za kirimbuzi, ariko avuga ko hakiri byinshi byo gukora kandi ko ibihano bigomba gukomeza kugeza Koreya ya Ruguru irangije kureka intwaro za kirimbuzi.
Ku wa gatatu Trump yavuze ko nta gihe ntarengwa cyo kubikora, kandi ko byatwara imyaka ibiri, itatu cyangwa itanu".
Ubushinwa n'Uburusiya birimo kuganira ku kibazo cy'uko akanama k'umutekano ka ONU kagomba guha Pyongyang ibihembo kubera ingamba zafashe.
Ariko, ku wa kane, umunyamabanga wa leta y'Amerika, Mike Pompeo, yabwiye inama y'umutekano y'umuryango w'abibumbye ko: "Ibihano by'inama y'umutekano bigomba gukomeza gushyirwa mu bikorwa nta nkomyi kandi nta n'ikintu na kimwe kirenzeho kugeza igihe tuzabona gukuraho burundu intwaro za kirimbuzi".
Akanama k'Umutekano kw'Isi kari kafashe icyemezo cyo kongera ibihano kuri Koreya ya Ruguru kuva mu 2006 mu rwego rwo guhagarika inkunga ya gahunda za Pyongyang z'ibitwaro bya kirimbuzi bya nikleyeri n'ibirwanisho bya misile.
Pompeo yahuye na Ri ku ruhande rw'Inteko rusange y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, nyuma avuga ko azasubira i Pyongyang mu kwezi gutaha gutegura inama ya kabiri.
Pompeo yasuye Koreya ya Ruguru inshuro eshatu muri uyu mwaka, ariko urugendo rwe rwa nyuma ntirwabaye rwiza.
Yavuye i Pyongyang muri Nyakanga avuga ko yari yarateye imbere, amasaha make mbere yuko Koreya ya Ruguru imuhamya ko yakoze "ibyifuzo bya mafiya".
Mu nama na Moon mu kwezi kwa mbere, Koreya ya Ruguru yasezeranyije ko izahagarika ikigo cy'ibisasu bya misile kimwe n'ikigo cy'ingufu za nikeleyeri, mu gihe Amerika yaba yafashe ingamba zihuje n'ibyo.
Yavuze ko Kim yamubwiye ko "ingamba zihwanye" yasabaga ari umutekano Trump yasezeranyije muri Singapour kandi ko ari intambwe igana ku buryo bushya umubano na Washington.
Abanyeshuri bo muri kaminuza ya Harvard bari mu mahugurwa yo kuruhuka bihagije
Muri uyu mwaka, ishuri rishya rya kaminuza ya Harvard ririmo gukora gahunda yo gusinziriza abanyeshuri baryo bose kugira ngo barwanye umuco ukomeje gukwirakwira w'igitsina cy'umugabo wo kwiga ijoro ryose biturutse kuri caf√©ine.
Hari umuhanga wavumbuye ko abanyeshuri bo muri za kaminuza zo mu rwego rwo hejuru ku isi, akenshi usanga batazi ibintu by'ibanze by'ukuntu bakwitaho.
Charles Czeisler, umwarimu wigisha iby'indoro mu Ishuri rya Kaminuza ry'Ubuvuzi rya Harvard, akaba n'impuguke mu by'indwara zo gusinzira mu bitaro bya Brigham na Muller, yatekereje iki cyiciro, akaba atekereza ko ari cyo cya mbere muri Amerika.
Yatangiye ayo masomo nyuma yo gutanga ikiganiro ku ngaruka zo kubura ibitotsi ku bumenyi.
"Ku mpera y'amasomo, umukobwa umwe yaje arambwira ati 'kuki ibyo bintu byose nabimenyeshejwe mu mwaka wanjye wa nyuma?'
Yavuze ko nta muntu n'umwe wigeze amubwira akamaro ko gusinzira, ibyo bikaba byaranshimishije".
Iri somo, ryatangijwe bwa mbere muri uyu mwaka, ryigisha abanyeshuri ibintu by'ibanze ku bijyanye n'ukuntu kugira akamenyero keza ko kuryama bifasha mu mwuga wo kwiga no mu mikino, ndetse no mu mibereho myiza.
Paul Barreira, umwarimu w'indwara zo mu mutwe mu ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya Harvard akaba n'umuyobozi mukuru w'imirimo y'ubuzima muri kaminuza, yavuze ko kaminuza yafashe icyemezo cyo gutangiza amasomo nyuma yo kubona ko abanyeshuri bafite ikibazo gikomeye cyo kubura ibitotsi mu cyumweru.
Ikiganiro cy'isaha imwe kirimo imirimo inyuranye ihuza.
Mu gice kimwe, hari ifoto y'icyumba cy'ishuri, aho abanyeshuri bakandaga mu bikombe bya kawa, mu madirishya, mu mashyiga no mu bitabo kugira ngo bamenye ingaruka z'ikawaine n'urumuri, n'ukuntu kubura ibitotsi bigira ingaruka ku mikinire, ndetse n'akamaro ko kugira gahunda yo kuryama.
Mu kindi gice, abantu bigishijwe uburyo kubura ibitotsi by'igihe kirekire bishobora kongera ibyago byo kurwara umutima, indwara yo mu bwonko, kwiheba no kurwara kanseri.
Ikarita y'ishuri ifite ibishushanyo mbonera by'ishuri byashishikarije abanyeshuri gutekereza ku buzima bwabo bwa buri munsi.
"Twaje kumenya ko ibyo bitazahindura imyitwarire y'abanyeshuri ako kanya.
Ariko twizera ko bafite uburenganzira bwo kumenya aya makuru, kimwe n'uko natwe dufite uburenganzira bwo kumenya ingaruka z'itabi ku buzima bwacu".
Yakomeje avuga ko umuco wo kurara amajoro yose ukomeje kubaho, kandi ko ikoranabuhanga rigezweho n'igitutu cy'abanyeshuri cyo kubura ibitotsi ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi.
Yongeyeho ko kugira ngo abanyeshuri barinde kugira stress, umunaniro, guhangayika, ndetse no kugira ngo birinde kugira ibiro byinshi, bagomba gusinzira bihagije kandi bakabona ibitotsi bihagije, kuko iyo umuntu adafite ibitotsi bituma ubwonko bwe bugira inzara, bigatuma ahora ashonje.
Raymond So, umunyeshuri w'imyaka 19 ukomoka muri California wiga ibijyanye na shimi na fiziki, yafashije Prof. Czeisler mu gutegura amasomo ye nyuma yo kwitabira rimwe mu masomo ye umwaka ushize ubwo yari mu mwaka wa mbere muri Harvard.
Yavuze ko amasomo yamuhumuye amaso kandi ko yamuhaye imbaraga zo gushyiraho amasomo ku ishuri ryose.
Intambwe ikurikira, ni uko abanyeshuri bose barangije kaminuza bagomba kuzuza porogaramu imwe mbere yo kwinjira mu kigo cy'abahanga.
Umwarimu Czeisler yagiriye abanyeshuri inama yo gutekereza ku guhitamo gushyiraho isaha yo kujya kuryama, ndetse no kubyuka. Ni byiza kandi ko bamenya ingaruka mbi z " "umucyo w'ubururu " uturuka ku bigaragarira amaso ya elegitoroniki na urumuri rwa LED, rushobora guhungabanya imikorere y'umunsi kandi ugatuma umuntu adasinzira neza.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: igitego cya Menga gica intege abagabo ba Gerrard
Rangers yongeye guhura n'ikindi kibazo cy'agahinda ubwo Dolly Menga yateye umugongo ikipe ya Steven Gerrard yari yangiritse, bayitsinda 1-0 i Livingston.
Ikipe ya Ibrox yari ifite intego yo gutsinda ku kibuga ku ncuro ya mbere kuva batsinda 4-1 muri Gashyantare i St Johnstone, ariko ikipe ya Gary Holt yatumye Gerrard atsindwa inshuro ebyiri mu mikino 18 nk'umutoza, yatumye ikipe ye itwara amanota umunani ku ruhande rwa Hearts, bayoboye Ladbrokes Premiership, shampiyona ya Scottish.
Menga yaje ku kibuga mbere y'iminota irindwi ngo bakomeze, maze umurongo w'abakinnyi ba Rangers wari ufite umwuka muke, ntiwigeze utuma habaho guhuza.
Mu gihe Rangers yamanutse ku mwanya wa gatandatu, Livingston yazamutse ku mwanya wa gatatu, iri inyuma ya Hibernian gusa ku gitego kimwe.
Kandi bishobora kuba byarababaje cyane Rangers nyuma yuko umucamanza w'umurongo Calum Spence yagombaga kwitabwaho kubera igikomere cyo mu mutwe nyuma yo guterwa ikintu.
Gerrard yagize impinduka umunani ku ikipe yatsinze Ayr muri kimwe cya kabiri cy'irangiza cya Betfred Cup, igikombe cya shampiyona ya Scottish League.
Ku rundi ruhande, Holt yari mu ikipe ya Livingston 11 yabonye inota ku mitima mu cyumweru gishize kandi yari yishimiye uburyo itsinda ryayo ryiteguye ryatsinze abarwanyaga ikipe yayo buri gihe.
Rangers ishobora kuba yarigaruriye umupira, ariko Livingston yakoze byinshi igihe yari afite umupira.
Bashoboraga kuba batsinze mu minota ibiri gusa ubwo igitego cya mbere cya Menga cyatumaga Scott Pittman agera ku izamu rya Allan McGregor, ariko myugariro yatakaje amahirwe akomeye.
Igitego gikomeye cya Keaghan Jacobs cyageze kuri kapiteni Craig Halkett, ariko mugenzi we Alan Lithgow yashoboye gusa kumutsinda ku mukono wa kabiri.
Rangers yafashe ubutegetsi, ariko bigaragara ko bari bafite icyizere kurusha uko bizeraga ko bashobora gutsinda igitego cya kabiri.
Nta gushidikanya, Alfredo Morelos yumvaga ko bagomba kuba barafatiye penaliti ku munota wa 15 igihe we na Steven Lawless bahuraga, ariko umusifuzi, Steven Thomson, yirengagije ibirego bya Colombian.
