Almanac: umuhanga mu guhimba imibare yitwa Geiger
Noneho, ku ipaji y'igitabo cyacu cyitwa "Sunday Morning", ku itariki ya 30 Nzeri 1882, hashize imyaka 136 uyu munsi, kandi IGIHE... ni umunsi umuhanga mu by'imiterere w'ejo hazaza, Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger yavukiyeho mu Budage.
Geiger yaje gukora uburyo bwo gutahura no gupima imirasire y'imirasire y'ikirere, ari na byo byatumye habaho igikoresho cyitwa Geiger Counter.
Kuva icyo gihe, igipimo cya Geiger cyabaye kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi byaranze umuco wa pop, nk'urugero nko muri filimi yo mu 1950 yitwa "Bells of Coronado", ikinnyuzwamo na bamwe mu bahanga b'ibimasa Roy Rogers na Dale Evans:
Umugabo ati: "Ibyo ni ibiki mu isi?"
Rogers: "Ni metero ya Geiger, ikoreshwa mu kumenya ubutare bufite radioactive, nka uranium.
Iyo wambaye utwo ducurama, ushobora kumva ingaruka z'amabuye atwara urumuri aturuka mu birunga".
Evans: "Ndavuga nti 'niba ari byo, birasenya!'
"Hans" Geiger yapfuye mu mwaka wa 1945, hashize iminsi mike gusa agize imyaka 63.
