Urukingo rushya rwa kanseri rushobora kwigisha ubwirinzi bw'umubiri kumenya udukoko dufite ubwandu
Urukingo rushya rwa kanseri rushobora kwigisha ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri kubona ingirabuzimafatizo zidakora neza no kuzica
Urukingo rwigisha ubwirinzi bw'umubiri kumenya udukorwe dufite ikibazo nk'igice cy'ubuvuzi
Ubu buryo burimo gukura mu murwayi ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, zikaba zarashyizwe muri laboratwari
Bashobora kubona poroteyine isanzwe mu bwoko butandukanye bwa kanseri, bakayishyira mu mubiri
Urukingo rw'igerageza rurimo rwerekana ko rufite ingaruka nziza ku barwayi ba kanseri zitandukanye.
Umugore umwe wahawe urukingo rwigisha ubwirinzi bw'umubiri kumenya uturemangingo dufite ikibazo, yashoboye kubona kanseri ye y'intanga yabuze mu gihe cy'amezi arenga 18.
Ubwo buryo buzakoreshwa mu gufata ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri w'umurwayi, maze zikavugururwa muri laboratwari kugira ngo "zishobore kubona" poroteyine izwi ku bwoko butandukanye bwa kanseri yitwa HER2, hanyuma izo ngirabuzimafatizo zigaciwe.
Professeur Jay Berzofsky wo muri US National Cancer Institute i Bethesda, Maryland, yagize ati "Ibi tubonye bigaragaza ko dufite urukingo rwizewe cyane".
Porofeseri Berzofsky yavuze ko HER2 "itera kanseri zitandukanye", harimo iz'ibere, iz'igifu, iz'ibihaha ndetse n'iz'urwagashya.
Uburyo bumwe bwo kuvanaho insoro z'umubiri z'abarwayi no kubigisha uburyo bwo kurwanya kanseri, bwagaragaye ko bufasha mu kuvura ubwoko bumwe bwa kanseri yo mu maraso.
