SIDA: Ubushinwa butangaza ko abarwayi biyongereyeho 14%
Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko umubare w'abaturage babana n'ubwandu bwa virusi itera sida wiyongereyeho 14%.
Abategetsi mu by'ubuvuzi bavuga ko icyo cyorezo gifata abantu barenga 820.000 mu gihugu hose.
Mu gihembwe cya kabiri cya 2018 honyine, abantu 40.000 banduye Ebola.
Abenshi mu barwayi bashya bandura mu mibonano mpuzabitsina, bikaba bigaragaza ko habayeho impinduka ugereranyije n'abo hambere.
Ubusanzwe, virusi itera SIDA yandura mu bice bimwe by'u Bushinwa biturutse ku guterwa amaraso yanduye.
Nyamara, umubare w'abantu banduye virusi itera SIDA muri ubwo buryo wagabanutse ugereranyije na zeru, nk'uko byatangajwe n'abayobozi b'ubuzima mu Bushinwa mu nama yabereye mu ntara ya Yunnan.
Nyamara, mu gihe cy'umwaka umwe, umubare w'abantu bafite virusi itera SIDA mu Bushinwa wiyongereyeho abantu 100,000.
Kwanduza SIDA mu mibonano mpuzabitsina ni ikibazo gikomeye mu muryango w'abashinwa b'abahuje ibitsina.
Ubwiyunge bw'abahuje ibitsina bwashyizwe mu rwego rw'amategeko mu Bushinwa mu 1997, ariko bavuga ko ivangura ry'abahuje ibitsina ryogeye.
Kubera amahame yo mu gihugu, ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko hagati ya 70 na 90% by'abagabo baryamana n'abandi bagabo bazahita bashakana n'abagore.
Benshi mu barwayi bayandura bitewe no kudakora imibonano mpuzabitsina mu buryo bukwiriye.
Kuva mu 2003, leta y'Ubushinwa yiyemeje ko abantu bose bashobora guhabwa ubufasha mu kuvura virusi itera SIDA, mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki kibazo.
Maxine Waters ahakana ko umwe mu bakozi b'ibiro by'umukuru w'igihugu yashyize hanze amakuru y'abasenateri b'Abarepubulikani, ko ari "ibinyoma by'akazu" kandi ko ari "inyigisho z'ubugizi bwa nabi"
Ku wa gatandatu, Uhagarariye Amerika, Maxine Waters, yatangaje ibirego by'uko umwe mu bakozi be yashyize amakuru bwite ya ba senateri batatu bo mu ishyaka ry'Abarepubulikani ku mpapuro z'abadepite za Wikipedia.
Umunya-Democratie wo mu kinyamakuru cya Los Angeles Democrat yavuze ko ibyo bitangazo byatanzwe n'imbuga za internet n'abanyamakuru bo mu "iburyo bw'iburyo".
Waters yagize icyo abivugaho mu butumwa yacishije kuri Twitter.
Amakuru yatangajwe harimo aderesi bwite na nomero za telefoni z'abasenateri ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Lindsey Graham wo muri leta ya Carolina y'Amajyepfo, na Mike Lee na Orrin Hatch, bo muri leta ya Utah.
Aya makuru yavuzwe ku rubuga rwa interineti ku wa kane, ashyirwa ku mugaragaro n'umuntu utazwi uri ku musozi wa Capitol, icyicaro cya guverinoma ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, mu gihe cy'iburanisha ry'inteko ishinga amategeko ku birego by'imyifatire idahwitse ku mushingwamanza w'ikirenga w'Ubwongereza, Brett Kavanaugh.
Iki gitangazamakuru cyagaragaye nyuma gato y'uko abasenateri batatu babajije Kavanaugh.
Imbuga z'urubuga nkoranyambaga zirimo Gateway Pundit na RedState, zavuze ko aderesi ya IP igaragaza inkomoko y'inyandiko yari ifitanye isano n'ishami rya Waters kandi ko yashyize ahagaragara amakuru y'umukozi wa Waters, nk'uko Capitol Hill ibitangaza.
Waters yakomeje agira ati "Icyo kirego nta shingiro gifite kandi ni ikinyoma cyuzuye".
"Umukozi wanjye, ufite umwirondoro, amakuru ye bwite n'umutekano byagizwe ibanga kubera ibyo birego by'ibinyoma n'uburiganya, nta burenganzira na buke afite mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutanga ayo makuru.
Iki kirego kitagira gihamya ni ikinyoma cyambaye ubusa".
Amagambo ya Waters yahise atangira kunengwa kuri interineti, harimo n'uwahoze ari umunyamabanga ushinzwe itangazamakuru mu biro bya White House, Ari Fleischer.
Fleischer yaranditse ati "ibyo byakozwe mu buryo bwo kwihimura.
"Ibi byumvikanisha ko adafite imyumvire yo kuba umwe mu bagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko.
Mu gihe umuntu ahamwe n'icyaha atakoze, ntukagire umujinya.
Ntagomba kwigaragaza nk'umuntu utagira icyo yitaho.
Ntukagire ikibazo ku mpamvu zituma umuntu akurikirana ibyo akurikiranye.
Agomba gukomeza kurangwa n'ubwitonzi n'amahoro".
