Johnny English Strikes Again, igitaramo cy'umusifuzi utagira imbaraga cya Rowan Atkinson
Ni ibisanzwe gushaka ko Brexit ihita igaragara muri firime nshya mu buryo bw'Abongereza kandi bisa nkaho ibyo bishobora gushyirwa ku kugaruka kwa filime y'urukozasoni ya Johnny English, yatangiye muri 2003 na Johnny English maze agaruka mu buzima muri 2011 na Johnny English Reborn (Johnny English Returns).
Ese ibyo byaba ari ugusebanya kw'urukozasoni ku bihereranye n'ukuntu turi abapfapfa by'ukuri, ku bihereranye n'uburyo bushya bwo gutumiza ibintu mu mahanga?
Ariko kandi, Johnny English, umuntu w'umunyabwenge, ufite amaso atukura kandi wambaye ubusa, yongeye guhabwa uruhushya rwo gusenya ibintu ku ncuro ya kabiri.
Birumvikana ko ari umupolisi w'umupfu, w'umwirasi, nubwo afite ibyo avuga byose, ufite Clouseau, n'imvugo ya Mr. Bean, n'urugero rw'umuntu wagize uruhare mu ndirimbo imwe mu ndirimbo z'amagare y'umuriro mu birori byo gutangiza imikino Olempike y'i Londres 2012.
Nanone kandi, mu mizo ya mbere ishingiye ku muntu mpuzamahanga w'isi yose kandi w'amayobera, Atkinson yigeze gukina mu matangazo ya televiziyo ya Barclaycard ubu yari yaribagiwe, aho yateje akaduruvayo mu nzira ye.
Hari ibihe byiza by'iminota mike mu mukino wa nyuma wa Johnny English.
Nkunda ukuntu Johnny English yegera kajugujugu yambaye imyambaro yo mu gihe cya kera, maze intambwe z'ikirere cy'iyo kajugujugu zikamushwanyaguza mu gice cy'imbere cy'iyo kajugujugu.
Impano ya Atkinson yo gusetsa umubiri iragaragara, ariko itanga igitekerezo cyuko urwenya rufite imbaraga nke kandi ni imfabusa bidasanzwe, cyane cyane mugihe bene filime "zikomeye", nka 007 na Mission Impossible, zimaze gukoresha urwenya muburyo bukomeye nka kimwe mubyungo byazo.
Birasa nkaho urwenya rwerekejwe ku bana, aho kuba abakuru, kandi, mubitekerezo byanjye, ibishuko bya Johnny English bitumvikana kandi ntibigomba kuba byitondewe nka byabindi bya film ya Atkinson itavuga igihe yabaga agaragaza imiterere ya Bean.
Noneho, impaka zihoraho ni uko Ubwongereza bufite ibibazo bikomeye.
Umunyamakuru wa interineti yinjiye mu kigo cy'ubutasi bw'Abongereza, ahishura amazina y'abakozi bose b'Abongereza bari muri ako karere, ku buryo byababaje cyane umukozi w'akazi, agace gato k'incuti y'agahenge yitwa Kevin Eldon.
Ni iherezo ry'umushikiranganji wa mbere w'umunyagitugu kandi ufite amakimbirane, ubu uri guhura n'ikibazo cyo kudakundwa na politiki: Emma Thompson arakora neza cyane muri uyu mwigeme usa nka Theresa May, ariko nta byinshi wakora kuri script.
Abajyanama be b'iperereza bamubwiye ko kubera ko intasi zose z'abakoraga muri icyo gihugu zagiye mu butasi, ko agomba kuzana umuntu wo mu za bukuru.
Kandi ibyo byerekeza ku muntu udashoboye Johnny English, ubu ukora nk'umwarimu mu kigo runaka cya snob, ariko akajya yigisha ku buryo budafite ireme uburyo bwo kuba umukozi w'ubutasi; muri iki gice harimo udutwenge duke, igihe English atanga ishuri ry'abacengezi ku ishuri ry'umuziki wa rock.
Bafashe English bamusubiza i Whitehall mu nama yihutirwa, maze ahura na mugenzi we Bough, wongeye gukina na Ben Miller.
Bough ubu ni umugabo wubatse ufite kapiteni wa ubwato bw'amato y'inyanja, ni umukinnyi w'umunyamwuga Vicki Pepperdine ari gutakaza.
Bateman na Robin bari barirengagijwe n'abakozi ba Nyir'ubwami, bashubije agatima mu kazi, maze bahura n'umugore mwiza cyane witwa Ophelia Bulletova, ukomoka kuri Olga Kurylenko.
Hagati aho, Minisitiri w'intebe arimo gutwarwa mu buryo buteye ubwoba n'igitekerezo cy'umuhanga mu ikoranabuhanga w'umuhanga mu guhanga udushya twinshi avuga ko ashobora gukemura ibibazo by'ikoranabuhanga mu Bwongereza: Jason Volta w'umunyamatsiko, ukina na Jake Lacy.
English na Bough batangiye urugendo rwabo rw'urukozasoni rw'urukozasoni: bambaye nk'abakozi bo mu nzu, batwika resitora y'Abafaransa; bateje akajagari babajyana mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko ku bwato bwa Volta; kandi English atangiza akajagari kose igihe agerageza gukoresha ibyuma by'ukuri by'ukuri kugirango amenye imbere mu nzu ya Volta.
Birumvikana ko ibyo byaha byose byakozwe bivuye muri iyi nkuru, ariko mu buryo bwiza kandi bugayitse, bisa nkaho byavuye muri televiziyo y'abana.
