Bityo, abakozi bashoboraga kumara iminsi itatu mu mpera z'icyumweru, ariko bagakomeza guhembwa umushahara.
Abaturage bavuga ko icyo gitekerezo "gihuje" n'umugambi w'ishyaka ku by'ubukungu ndetse n'imigambi yo guhindura igihugu kigana ku ruhande rw'abakozi.
Ishyirahamwe ry'abakozi ku kazi ryashyigikiye ko amasaha y'akazi y'iminsi ine mu cyumweru aba ari ingamba zo gufasha abakozi kwiteza imbere mu gihe ubukungu buhinduka.
Umuntu ukomeye mu ishyaka ry'abakozi yabwiye The Sunday Times ati: "Twiteze ko politiki nshya izatangazwa mbere y'impera z'uyu mwaka.
"Ntabwo bizasohora mu ijoro rimwe, ariko icyumweru cy'akazi cy'iminsi ine ni intego ijyanye n'uburyo ishyaka rigamije guhuza ubukungu ku bw'umukozi, kimwe n'uburyo bw'ishyaka rusange bw'ishyaka".
Ishyaka ry'abakozi ntiriba ari irya mbere mu gushyigikira icyo gitekerezo, kuko ishyaka ry'abirabura ryahise ryemeza ko hazabaho icyumweru cy'akazi cy'iminsi ine mu gihe cy'amatora rusange yo mu 2017.
Ariko, ubu ishyaka ry'abakozi ntirifasha ishyaka ry'ishyaka ryose.
Umuvugizi w'ishyaka ry'abakozi yagize ati "Icyumweru cy'akazi k'iminsi ine ntabwo kiri muri politiki y'ishyaka kandi ntabwo kiri mu bigenderwaho n'iri shyaka".
Umunyamabanga w'ishyaka John McDonnell yifashishije ikoraniro ry'ishyaka ry'abakozi mu cyumweru gishize mu gushimangira icyerekezo cye cy'impinduramatwara y'abashoramari mu bukungu.
Bwana McDonnell yavuze ko yari yariyemeje kongera kuyobora "abayobozi batamenyekanye" n' "abatekamutwe" mu bigo by'abikorera.
Gahunda z'umushoramari wo mu gicucu kandi zivuga ko hari amahirwe ko abafite imigabane muri sosiyete z'amazi batazabona amafaranga yabo yose, kuko leta y'abakozi ishobora "kugabanya" kubera amakosa avugwa.
Yemeje kandi gahunda yo gushyira abakozi mu nama z'amasosiyete no gushyiraho amafaranga y'umutungo w'ibanze yo guha 10% by'imigabane y'ibigo by'abikorera ku bakozi, byinjiza amafaranga y'inyungu y'umwaka angana n'amapawundi 500.
Lindsey Graham na John Kennedy babwiye 60 Minutes niba iperereza rya FBI kuri Kavanaugh ryaba ryaratumye bahindura ibitekerezo
