Ku cyumweru, mu kiganiro cy'ikiganiro, umunyamakuru wa "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley yabajije abasenateri John Kennedy na Lindsey Graham bo mu ishyaka ry'Abarepubulikani niba FBI yashobora kuvumbura ikintu cyatuma bahindura ibitekerezo byabo.
Kennedy yagaragaje ko yivugishaga kurusha mugenzi we wo muri Carolina y'amajyepfo.
Kennedy ati "Ni byo koko.
"Narababwiye ko nzajya mu rukiko.
Namuhamagaye nyuma y'uko ibyo birego byatangajwe, maze mubaza niba yari yabikoreye.
