Ariko kandi, uko bigaragara, Graham nta cyo yahindura ku mwanzuro we.
Yagize ati "Ibitekerezo byanjye kuri Brett Kavanaugh birakomeye kandi byantera guturika".
"Dr. Ford, sinzi uko byagenze; ariko icyo nzi ni iki: Brett yarabyanze yivuye inyuma", Graham yongeyeho yerekeza kuri Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kandi abo wavuze ntibashoboye kugenzura ibyo wavuze.
