Ni iki Global Citizen Festival yakoze mu kurwanya ubukene?
Kuri uyu wa gatandatu, New York izaba yakiriye ibirori by'umuziki ngarukamwaka byitwa Global Citizen Festival, birimo ibitaramo bikomeye by'abahanzi b'ibirangirire bazakora kandi bafite intego yo kurandura ubukene ku isi.
Mu mwaka wa karindwi, Global Citizen Festival izareba abantu ibihumbi n'ibihumbi bazaza mu gace ka Great Lawn muri Central Park, atari gusa kwishimira ibikorwa nka Janet Jackson, Cardi B na Shawn Mendes, ahubwo no gukangurira abantu intego nyayo y'iki gikorwa cyo kurandura ubukene mbere ya 2030.
Global Citizen Festival yatangiye mu mwaka wa 2012, ni ubufatanye bw'umuryango w'abaterankunga mpuzamahanga, Global Poverty Project, wifuza gukuraho ubukene mu kwongera umubare w'abantu bakora ibikorwa byo kubirwanya.
Kugirango ubone itike yo kwinjira kubuntu (keretse niba ushaka kwishyura itike ya VIP), abitabiriye bagomba kuzuza ibikorwa byinshi cyangwa "ibikorwa", nko gukora ubushake, kohereza imeri kumutegetsi wisi, guterefona cyangwa ubundi buryo bwingenzi bwo gufasha kumenyekanisha intego yo kurandura ubukene.
Ariko se, ni mu rugero rungana iki Global Citizen yageze ku ntego yayo mu myaka 12 ishize?
Ese guha abantu ibihembo by'igitaramo ku buntu ni uburyo bwo kwemeza abantu kugira ngo bagire icyo bakora cyangwa ni ikindi kibazo cy'abantu bitwa "abakora umwuga", abantu bibwira ko bashobora guhindura ibintu binyuze mu gushyira umukono ku nyandiko y'inyandiko isaba ko ibintu byahindurwa cyangwa binyuze mu butumwa bwo kuri Twitter?
Kuva mu mwaka wa 2011, Global Citizen ivuga ko imaze kubona "ibikorwa" birenga miliyoni 19 by'abayoboke bayo, ikora ibikorwa bitandukanye.
Avuga ko ibyo bikorwa byafashije abayobozi bo ku isi gutangaza imihigo na politiki bingana na miliyari 37 z'amadolari yashyizweho kugira ngo bigire ingaruka ku buzima bw'abantu barenga miliyoni 2,250 mbere ya 2030.
Mu ntangiriro za 2018, itsinda ryavuze imihigo 390 n'amatangazo aturuka ku bikorwa byayo, aho nibura miliyari 10 z'amadolari yamaze gutangwa cyangwa gukusanywa.
Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ibihe by'Imibereho Myiza (ABI) cyatangaje ko kugeza ubu, amafaranga y'ingoboka yageze ku bantu bagera kuri miriyoni 649 ku isi.
Bimwe mu byemezo by'ingenzi byashyizweho harimo The Power of Nutrition, umuryango w'abashoramari n'abakora umwuga wo gutunga ibyokurya mu Bwongereza biyemeje "gufasha abana kugera ku bushobozi bwabo bwose", basezeranya kuzaha u Rwanda miliyoni $35 zo gufasha mu kurwanya imirire mibi mu gihugu nyuma yo kwakira ubutumwa bugera kuri 4700 bw'umunyamakuru wa Global Citizen.
"Ku bufatanye na leta y'Ubwongereza, abatanga inkunga, abayobozi b'ibihugu n'abashyigikiye Global Citizen nkawe, dushobora guhindura akarengane ku buzima bw'abantu bafite ikibazo cy'imirire mibi mu mateka", ibyo ni ko ambasaderi wa The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, yabwiye imbaga y'abantu mu gitaramo cyabereye i Londres mu kwezi kwa kane mu mwaka wa 2018.
Iri tsinda kandi ryavuze ko nyuma y'ibikorwa birenga 5000 byo kuzamura imirire y'ababyeyi n'abana mu Bwongereza, guverinoma yatangaje inkunga y'umushinga The Power of Nutrition, uzafasha abagore n'abana miliyoni 5 mu bijyanye n'imirire.
Mu gusubiza ikibazo gikunda kubazwa ku rubuga rwabo, "Ni iki gituma mutekereza ko dushobora kuvanaho ubukene bukabije?"
Global Citizen yarashubije iti "Ubwo ni inzira ndende kandi itoroshye, kandi hari igihe tuzagwa tukagwa.
Ariko nk'uko byagenze ku myigaragambyo ikomeye yo kurwanya ivangura no guharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu byabanjirije, tuzabishobora, kuko dufatanyije, turakomeye.
Janet Jackson, the Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B na Janelle Monae ni bamwe mu bahanzi bazagaragara muri iki gitaramo kizabera i New York, kizatangwa na Deborra-Lee Furness na Hugh Jackman.
Amerika ishobora gukoresha ingabo zayo mu guhagarika ibicuruzwa by'ingufu by'Uburusiya, nkuko Minisitiri w'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu muri Amerika yabivuze
"Niba ari ngombwa", Washington ishobora gukoresha inyanja mu kwirinda ko amashanyarazi y'u Burusiya agera ku masoko, harimo n'ayo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, nkuko byatangajwe n'umunyamabanga wa Amerika ushinzwe ububanyi n'amahanga, Ryan Zinke, nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikinyamakuru Washington Examiner.
Zinke yavuze ko Uburusiya bufite uruhare muri Syria, cyane cyane aho bukorera ku nkunga ya leta yemewe, ari urwitwazo rwo gushakisha amasoko mashya y'ingufu.
"Ndumva impamvu bari mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati ari uko bashaka kugirana amasezerano y'ingufu nk'uko babikoze mu Burayi bw'iburasirazuba", nk'uko bivugwa ko yabivuze.
Byongeye kandi, nk'uko uwo muofisiye yabivuze, bafite uburyo n'uburyo bwo guhangana na byo.
Yagize ati "Amerika ifite ubushobozi, ifatanyije n'ingabo zayo z'ingabo, bwo kugenzura ko inzira zo mu mazi zifunguye, kandi, mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, ikazifunga kugira ngo izamure ingufu zayo zitajya ku isoko".
Zinke yabwiye abitabiriye uyu muhango wateguwe n'ishyirahamwe ry'abakiliya b'ingufu, ryishyize hamwe ryitwa "ijwi ry'abakoresha ingufu" muri Amerika.
Yagereranyije ingamba za Washington zo guhangana n'Uburusiya na Irani, azirikana ko mu by'ukuri ari kimwe.
Yagize ati "Ihitamo ry'ubukungu muri Irani n'Uburusiya ni ugufata no gusimbuza ibikomoka kuri peteroli", mu gihe yerekezaga ku Burusiya avuga ko "bufite uburyo bumwe gusa" n'ubukungu bushingiye kuri peteroli.
Ibyo byavuzwe mu gihe ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwari mu gikorwa cyo guteza imbere ibicuruzwa byoherezwa mu Burayi biturutse ku isuka ry'ibikomoka kuri gaz, mu rwego rwo gusimbura ibikomoka ku isuka y'Uburusiya, ari na yo yo mahitamo yoroheje ku bakoresha b'i Burayi.
Kugira ngo ibyo bigerweho, abayobozi b'ubutegetsi bwa Trump, harimo na perezida ubwe, bagerageje kwemeza u Budage guhagarika umushinga w'umuyoboro wa Nord Stream 2 "udakwiriye", aho Trump yavuze ko Berlin yahindutse "imfungwa" ya Moscou.
Moscow yakomeje gushimangira ko umuyoboro wa Nord Stream 2 w'amadolari miliyari 11 z'amadolari, wateganyijwe gukwirakwiza umuyoboro w'amazi ufite ubushobozi bwo gutwara metero kibe 110 z'amadolari, ari umushinga w'ubukungu gusa.
Kremlin yavuze ko Washington yanze iyo gahunda kubera impamvu z'ubukungu gusa, kandi ko ari urugero rw'amarushanwa adahuje.
"Ntekereza ko dusangiye igitekerezo cy'uko ingufu zidashobora kuba igikoresho cyo gushyiraho igitutu, kandi ko abakoresha ingufu bagomba kuba bemerewe guhitamo abazitanga", Minisitiri w'Ingufu w'u Burusiya, Aleksandr Novak, yabivuze nyuma y'inama yagiranye n'Umunyamabanga wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika ushinzwe ingufu, Rick Perry, yabaye muri Nzeri i Moscou.
Imyanzuro ya Amerika yatumye u Budage bwongera gushimangira ko bwiyemeje gushyiraho iyo gahunda.
Ishyirahamwe ry'abashoramari mu Budage, BDI, ryasabye Amerika kuva muri politiki y'ingufu z'Uburayi no kuva mu masezerano y'ubufatanye hagati ya Berlin na Moscou.
Dieter Kempf, umuyobozi wa BDI, nyuma y'inama iherutse kuba hagati ya Angela Merkel n'umukuru w'u Burusiya, Vladimir Putin, yagize ati: "Mfite ikibazo gikomeye iyo igihugu cya gatatu cyinjiye mu bikoresho byacu by'ingufu".
Elizabeth Warren azasuzuma yitonze niba azashaka kuba Perezida mu 2020, nk'uko bivugwa na senateri w'intara ya Massachusetts
Ku wa Gatandatu, Senateri Elizabeth Warren wa Massachusetts yavuze ko azasuzuma yitonze niba azatanga kandidatire ye mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu nyuma y'amatora yo mu kwezi kwa kabiri.
