"Igihe kirageze ngo abagore bajye i Washington bakore ibishoboka byose ngo bagire guverinoma ibogamye kandi ibyo birimo umugore uri ku butegetsi", nkuko The Hill ibitangaza.
"Kuva ku itariki ya 6 Ugushyingo nzasuzuma mbyitondeye niba koko nshobora kwiyamamariza kuba Perezida".
Warren yagize icyo avuga kuri Perezida Donald Trump mu nama rusange, avuga ko "ari kuyobora iki gihugu mu cyerekezo kitari cyo.
