Ibihugu 18 n'Akarere ka Columbia biyamiriza politiki nshya y'ubuhunzi
Leta 18 n'Umurenge wa Columbia byatanze ikirego mu nkiko ku itegeko rishya ry'Amerika ribuza ubuhungiro ku bahunga urugomo mu ngo cyangwa mu miryango y'abagizi ba nabi.
Ku wa Gatanu w'icyumweru gishize, abahagarariye leta 18 n'akarere ka Washington batanze raporo yo gushyigikira umushaka w'ubuhungiro urwanya politiki, nk'uko NBC News yabitangaje.
Izina ryuzuye ry'umutangabuhamya mu rubanza Sessions de Grace v. rw'ishyirahamwe ry'Abanyagihugu bo mu Burenganzira bw'Abaturage muri Amerika rwasuzuguye politiki ya leta muri Kanama ntiryatangajwe.
Yavuze ko umugore we "n'abana be bagize umuryango w'ibyaha by'urugomo" bamukoreye ihohoterwa, ariko ko abayobozi ba Amerika banze ubusabe bwe bw'ubuhunzi ku ya 20 Nyakanga.
Bafatiwe muri Texas.
Abunganira Grace mu mategeko bavuga ko El Salvador, Honduras na Guatemala, ibihugu byandujwe n'umubare munini w'abasaba ubuhungiro muri Amerika, byugarijwe n'ibibazo by'ubugizi bwa nabi bw'ibiturage n'ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo.
Gahunda nshya y'ubuhungiro muri Amerika yasimbuye icyemezo cy'umwaka wa 2014 cy'akanama gashinzwe ubuhungiro ko kwemerera abimukira badafite ibyangombwa bahunga urugomo rwo mu ngo zabo gusaba ubuhungiro.
Umushinjacyaha mukuru w'intara ya Columbia, Karl Racine, yavuze mu itangazo ku wa gatanu ko iyo politiki nshya "yirengagije ibimaze imyaka mirongo bihari mu mategeko ya leta, ay'igihugu n'ay'amahanga".
Raporo y'urukiko yasobanuye igira iti "itegeko rya leta risaba ko abantu bose basaba ubuhungiro bahabwa indishyi hakurikijwe imiterere n'imiterere nyayo y'ibyo basabye, kandi iryo tegeko rivuguruza iryo hame".
Abashinjacyaha bakomeje impaka mu cyegeranyo ko politiki yo kwanga ko abimukira binjira mu gihugu yangiza ubukungu bwa Amerika, basobanura ko bishoboka ko bazavamo ba rwiyemezamirimo kandi "bagatanga abakozi".
Mu kwezi kwa gatandatu, umushinjacyaha mukuru Jeff Sessions yategetse abacamanza bo mu nzego z'abimukira kudatanga ubuhungiro ku bantu bahunga ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo n'urugomo rw'amashyirahamwe y'abagizi ba nabi.
"Ubuhungiro buhabwa abantu bavuye mu gihugu cyabo kubera gutotezwa cyangwa gutinya kubera ubwoko, idini, ubwenegihugu cyangwa kuba mu itsinda runaka cyangwa ibitekerezo bya politiki", Sessions yatangaje mu itangazo rye rya politiki ryo ku ya 11 Kamena.
Ntabwo ubuhungiro bwigeze bugamije gukemura ibibazo byose (ndetse n'ibibazo bikomeye) abantu bahura nabyo buri munsi ku isi.
Abatabazi b'impunzi mu mujyi wa Palu mu gihe umubare w'abapfuye wiyongereye cyane mu gihe abantu benshi bari mu rujijo
Ku barokotse, ibintu biragenda birushaho kuba bibi.
"Imimerere irahangayitse cyane", niko Risa Kusuma, umubyeyi w'imyaka 35 yavuze, aho yari ahumurije umwana we wari urwaye umuriro mu kigo cy'ubuhungiro mu mujyi wa Palu waguye mu mpanuka.
"Raba uko ambulances z'abapfuye zisohoka buri munota.
Kandi amazi meza ntiboneka cyane".
Abaturage babonetse bagaruka mu mazu yabo yasenyutse, batoragura ibintu byabo by'ibyabo byari byamenetse, bagerageza kurokora ikintu cyose bashoboye kubona.
Abantu babarirwa mu magana bakomeretse, kandi ibitaro by'abamaze kwangirika n'umutingito ufite ubukana bwa 7.5, byuzuye.
Bamwe mu bakomeretse, barimo Dwi Haris, wavunitse umugongo n'igitsintsiri, bari baruhukiye hanze y'Ibitaro bya Gisirikare bya Palu, aho abarwayi bavurirwaga hanze kubera imitingito y'urudaca.
Amarira yamuzuye mu maso igihe yasobanuraga uko yumvaga ameze igihe umutingito ukaze w'isi wibasiraga icyumba cya hoteli yari atuyemo n'umugore we n'umwana wabo, cyari mu igorofa ya gatanu.
"Nta gihe cyo kurokora ubuzima bwacu cyari gihari.
Ibisigazwa by'urukuta byaranshenye, ndatekereza", Haris yabwiye Associated Press, yongeraho ko umuryango we wari mu bukwe mu mujyi.
"Nateze amatwi umugore wanjye, mu ijwi riranguruye, nyuma yaho ndaceceka.
Sinzi ibyabaye kuri we cyangwa ku mukobwa wanjye.
Nizeye ko nta byago byabagwiririye".
Ambasaderi wa Amerika ashinja Ubushinwa gukoresha nabi "amatangazo y'ibinyoma"
Nyuma y'icyumweru kimwe ikinyamakuru cy'u Bushinwa cyasohoye itangazo ry'amapaji ane mu kinyamakuru cyo muri Amerika, ryamamaza inyungu z'ubucuruzi hagati y'Amerika n'u Bushinwa, Ambasaderi wa Amerika mu Bushinwa, ashinja u Bushinwa gukoresha ikinyamakuru cy'Amerika mu gukwirakwiza poropagande.
Perezida wa Amerika, Donald Trump, yagarutse ku kinyamakuru cy'ubwishyu cya China Daily mu kinyamakuru Des Moines Register, ikinyamakuru kigurishwa cyane muri leta ya Iowa, nyuma yo gushinja u Bushinwa kwivanga mu matora y'abadepite muri Amerika azaba ku itariki ya 6 y'uku kwezi kwa cumi na kumwe, ibintu Ubushinwa buhakana.
Trump ashinja Beijing ko irimo kugerageza kwivanga mu matora yo muri Amerika, byatangaje icyo abategetsi b'Amerika babwiye Reuters ko ari igice gishya cya gahunda y'i Washington yo gukandamiza u Bushinwa.
Nubwo ari ibisanzwe ko za leta z'amahanga zashyiraho amatangazo yo guteza imbere ubucuruzi, Beijing na Washington ubu bari mu ntambara y'ubucuruzi igenda yiyongera, ibi bikaba byerekana ko ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa byinjira mu mahanga biri hejuru.
Nkuko byemezwa n'abahanga bo mu Bushinwa no muri Amerika, ibihano by'Ubushinwa mu ntambara y'ubucuruzi yari igamije kubangamira ibihugu bitanga umusaruro nka Iowa, ishyigikiye ishyaka rya Trump ry'Abarepubulika.
Terry Branstad, ambasaderi wa Amerika mu Bushinwa, akaba n'uwahoze ari guverineri wa Iowa, kimwe mu bihugu by'u Bushinwa bitumiza umusaruro w'ubuhinzi, yavuze ko Beijing yangije abakozi, abahinzi n'abacuruzi b'Abanyamerika.
Mu nyandiko y'ibitekerezo yanditswe na Branstad yasohotse mu kinyamakuru cyo ku cyumweru cy'ikinyamakuru Moines Register, yavuze ko u Bushinwa "burimo bwiyongera muri ubu bucuruzi bwo guhohotera abantu binyuze mu gutangaza amatangazo yo kwamamaza mu binyamakuru by'Abanyamerika bitanga ibinyamakuru".
"Mu gukwirakwiza poropagande yayo, leta y'Ubushinwa ikoresha umuco w'Amerika wo kuvuga no gutangaza amakuru mu gutanga itangazo ryishyurwa muri Des Moines Register", Branstad yaranditse.
"Ahubwo, mu kabari k'ibinyamakuru gaherereye mu mpera y'umuhanda wo muri Beijing, nta majwi menshi atandukanye yumvikana kandi nta n'igaragaza neza ibitekerezo binyuranye Abashinwa bashobora kuba bafite ku ngendo iteye impungenge y'ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa, kubera ko itangazamakuru riri munsi y'ubutegetsi bw'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti b'Ubushinwa".
Avuga kandi ko "ikinyamakuru kimwe gikomeye mu Bushinwa cyamwimye gutanga inyandiko" y'inkuru ye, ariko ntiyavuze ikinyamakuru cy'ukuri.
Kagame n'abambari be bari mu myigaragambyo yo kwamagana ubutegetsi bwa Kagame.
Nubwo benshi mu bayobozi bakomeye ba Repubulika bashyigikiye kandi bakanavuganira Brett Kavanaugh, umukandida w'Urukiko rw'Ikirenga, nubwo hari ibirego byinshi by'ihohotera rishingiye ku gitsina, abahanga mu gusesengura ibintu baravuga ko amatora y'umukuru w'igihugu azazana umujinya, cyane cyane uw'abagore.
Abarepubulikani benshi bitabiriye aya matora, kandi abenshi mu bayoboke b'ishyaka rya G20 barifuzaga ko amatora yakomeza.
Mu kiganiro cyasohotse ku cyumweru mu kinyamakuru The Hill, Grant Reeher, umwarimu w'ubumenyi bwa politiki muri kaminuza ya Maxwell, muri kaminuza ya Syracuse, yagize ati "Ibyo bintu ntibishobora gukurwaho.
Reeher kandi yavuze ko ashidikanya ko isaha ya nyuma ya Senateri Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ku iperereza rya FBI izarohereza abatora barakariye.
Karine Jean-Pierre, umujyanama mukuru n'umuvugizi w'ishyaka MoveOn, mu kinyamakuru cy'i Washington, D.C., yagize ati "abagore ntibazigera bibagirwa ibyabaye ejo, ndetse nta n'ubwo bazayibagirwa mu gihe kizaza cya vuba aha cyangwa mu kwezi kwa 11".
Ku wa Gatanu mu gitondo, abaturwanya, mu magambo ahimbye cyane ngo "Ugushyingo ruregereje!", bakoze imyigaragambyo mu cyumba cya Sena, mu gihe abarepubulikani bari ku butegetsi bwa Komite y'Ubucamanza, biyemeje gukomeza gushyiraho Kavanaugh, nubwo Dr. Christine Blasey Ford yari yabihamije, nk'uko Mic yabitangaje.
Stu Rothenberg, umwe mu basesenguzi b'impande zombi mu bya politiki, yabwiye urubuga rw'amakuru rwa The New York Times ati "Impamvu n'ishyaka by'abademokarate birenze ibyo umuntu yatekerezaga".
"Ni byo koko, uri muremure,
ariko biracyakomeza, cyane cyane mu bagore batarafata umwanzuro bo mu bice by'icyaro cyangwa abo mu kigero cy'imyaka 18-29, nubwo batakunda Perezida, ntibakunze kujya mu matora".
Mbere y'uko Ford atanga ubuhamya ku mugaragaro ku birego bye byo gusambanya umukandida w'Urukiko rw'Ikirenga, abahanga mu by'amategeko bavuze ko bishoboka ko habaho imyigaragambyo ikomeye mu gihe Abarepubulika bakomeje kwemeza.
