Uwatangije World Wide Web ashaka gukora interineti nshya ihangana na Google na Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, ari na we wavumbuye urubuga rwa interineti, atangiza uruganda rushya rwo guhatana na Facebook, Amazon na Google.
Inrupt, umushinga mushya w'uyu mugabo w'umuhanga mu ikoranabuhanga, ni ikigo gishingiye kuri Solid, urubuga rufunguye rwa Berners-Lee.
Solid iha abakoresha uburenganzira bwo guhitamo aho babika amakuru yabo n'abantu bashobora kuyabona.
Mu kiganiro cyihariye na Fast Company, Berners-Lee yavuze ko intego ya Inrupt ari "gutegeka isi".
"Tugomba kubikora", ni ko yavuze kuri iyo sosiyete.
"Iki ni igihe cy'amateka".
Porogaramu ikoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Solid kugirango abantu babashe gukora ububiko bwabo bwite "bw'ibanga bwo kuri interineti" cyangwa POD.
Birashobora kuba byanditseho urutonde rw'abo bavugana, urutonde rw'ibyo ugomba gukora, kalendari, umuziki n'ibindi bikoresho byawe bwite n'iby'umwuga.
Ni nk'aho Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack na Spotify byose byatangiye gukoreshwa muri browser imwe icyarimwe.
Ikidasanzwe kuri ubu bubiko bw'amakuru bwite ni uko buri mukoresha aba afite ububasha bwo kugenzura amakuru ye.
Icyo kigo cyita "guha abantu ubushobozi binyuze mu makuru".
Igitekerezo cya Inrupt, nk'uko umuyobozi wayo John Bruce abivuga, ni uko isosiyete itanga umutungo, imikorere n'ubushobozi bikwiye kugira ngo ifashe Solid kuba yagera ku isi hose.
Ubu iyi sosiyete igizwe na Berners-Lee, Bruce, sosiyete y'umutekano wa mudasobwa ya IBM, bamwe mu bahanga bahaye akazi gukora kuri uyu mushinga hamwe n'umuryango w'ababyitangiye.
Guhera muri iki cyumweru, abayikora ku isi yose bashobora kuzajya bakora porogaramu zabo bwite za mudasobwa bakoresheje ibikoresho biri ku rubuga rwa Inrupt.
Berners-Lee yatangaje ko yaba we cyangwa itsinda rye batigeze bavugana na "Facebook cyangwa Google ku bijyanye no gutangiza impinduka zose zishobora guhindura imodeli zabo z'ubucuruzi umunsi ku wundi.
"Ntidukeneye ko atubwira ibyo ari byo".
Mu nyandiko yasohotse ku wa gatandatu kuri Medium, Berners-Lee yanditse ko "Inrupt mission ari ugutanga imbaraga z'ubucuruzi n'ibidukikije bifasha kurinda ubusugire n'ubwiza bw'urubuga rushya rushingiye kuri Solid".
Mu mwaka wa 1994, Berners-Lee yahinduye internet ubwo yashingaga umuryango wa World Wide Web Consortium ku kigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cya Massachusetts.
Mu mezi make ashize, Berners-Lee yabaye ijwi rikomeye mu mpaka zo kutagira aho babogamira mu by'ikoranabuhanga.
Ndetse no mugihe cyo gutangiza Inrupt, Berners-Lee aracyari umukozi washinzwe kandi akaba umuyobozi wumuryango wa World Wide Web Consortium, kimwe n'imiryango ya Web Foundation na Open Data Institute.
Berners-Lee yagize ati "mfite icyizere gikomeye kuri iyi si nshya ya internet".
Tribute to Bernard Vann, umupasiteri wahawe umusaraba w'ishimwe mu ntambara ya mbere y'isi yose
Umupadiri umwe rukumbi wo mu Itorero ry'Abangilikani wahawe agashimwe ka Victoria Cross mu ntambara ya mbere y'isi, yashyizwe ku mugaragaro mu mujyi w'iwabo nyuma y'imyaka 100.
Lieutenant Colonel na Reverend Bernard Vann yahawe igihembo cyo ku ya 29 Nzeri 1918, mu gitero cya Bellenglise na Lehaucourt.
Ariko, yishwe n'umushinjacyaha nyuma y'iminsi ine atazi ko yahawe icyubahiro gikomeye cya gisirikare cy'Abongereza.
Ku wa gatandatu, abuzukuru be babiri bashyize ahagaragara urwibutso mu cyubahiro cye mu birori i Rushden (Northamptonshire).
Michael Vann, umwe mu buzukuru be, yagaragaje ko ari ibintu by'ingenzi cyane kuba yaravumbuye icyo kibanza nyuma y'imyaka 100 gusa nyuma y'ibyo sekuru yakoze, byatumye ahabwa iryo zina.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikinyamakuru cyitwa London Gazette, ku itariki ya 29 Nzeri 1918, Lieutenant Colonel Vann yayoboye umutwe w'ingabo ze mu muyoboro wa Saint-Quentin "mu gihu cyinshi no mu gihe cy'umuriro mwinshi w'imbunda".
Nyuma yaho yihutiye kugera ku murongo w'umuriro maze, "n'ubutwari bwinshi", ayobora umurongo imbere mbere yo kwiruka n'imbunda kandi nta bufasha bw'umuntu n'umwe, no guhitana abantu batatu bo mu itsinda ry'umwanzi.
Lieutenant Colonel Vann yishwe n'Umudage wari umufashe mu buryo butunguranye ku ya 4 Ukwakira 1918, hasigaye ukwezi kumwe ngo intambara irangire.
Michael Vann w'imyaka 72 yavuze ko ibyo sekuru yakoze ari "ikintu ntashoboraga kubaho, ariko ni isomo".
We n'umuvandimwe we Dr James Vann nabo bashyizeho ikamba ry'indabyo nyuma y'igitaramo, cyayobowe n'itsinda ry'urubyiruko Brentwood Imperial.
Michael Vann yavuze ko "yaterwaga ishema no kuba yari mu birori byo kwambara imyenda y'abagabo" yongeraho ko "ubutwari bw'uyu ntwari nyakuri bugaragazwa n'ukuntu abantu benshi bamushyigikiye".
Peppa Pig yahaye icyuho abafana ba MMA mu gihe cyiza
