Yagize ati "Iyo ubajije umwaka ushize, impamvu ikomeye yanteraga ni ugutsinda ikamba rya zahabu".
Ariko ubu nzi ko hari ibindi bintu by'ingenzi cyane kuruta umudari wa zahabu wo mu mikino ya Olempike.
Kuri njyewe, umudari wanjye ni Robbie".
