Umwaka wakurikiyeho, Daley yitabiriye imikino ya Olempike ya 2012 maze yegukana umudali w'umuringa.
Yagize ati "Icyo gihe namenye ko ari cyo cyifuzo cyanjye cy'ubuzima bwanjye: gusimbuka imbere y'imbaga y'abantu mu gihugu cyanjye nkajya mu mikino Olempike, nta byiyumvo byiza by'ibyo nari mfite".
