Mickelson wari utameze neza ku buryo yari ku kibuga cy'irushanwa ry'igikombe cya Ryder Cup kuri uyu wa Gatandatu
Umunyamerika Phil Mickelson azatangaza amateka kuri iki cyumweru ubwo azakina umukino wa 47 wa Ryder Cup, ariko agomba kongera ubuhanga bwe kugira ngo bitazahinduka ibyago.
Mickelson, uri mu marushanwa ngarukamwaka ku nshuro ya 12, yahagaritswe ku bw'icyemezo cya kapiteni Jim Furyk, ntiyabasha kwitabira imikino ya fourball cyangwa foursomes yo ku wa gatandatu.
Aho kugira ngo abe ari we uhagarariye Amerika nk'uko byari bimeze mu bihe byinshi mbere, uyu mugabo w'ibyamamare mu mikino y'igikombe cy'isi inshuro eshanu, yamaraga umunsi wose yishimye kandi akora ibishoboka byose ngo yongere imbaraga mu mikino.
Nubwo atigeze aba umukinnyi w'umuhanga, ndetse no mu gihe cy'umwuga we, ku myaka ye 48 ntabwo ahuye n'ikibuga cya Le Golf National, aho ubwatsi burebure bukunze guhana abakinnyi baguye mu makosa.
Kandi niba ibyo bidahagije, Mickelson azahura ku munsi w'ejo ku mukino wa 9 na Francesco Molinari, wegukanye British Open, ufatanyije na Tommy Fleetwood gutsinda imikino ine yose y'iki cyumweru.
Niba Amerika, amanota ane hasi mu mikino 12 y'irushanwa ry'igikombe cy'isi, itangiye neza, umukino wa Mickelson ushobora kuba uw'ingenzi cyane.
Furyk yari afitiye icyizere umuntu we, nubwo nta kindi yashoboraga kuvuga.
Furyk yagize ati "yasobanukiwe neza uruhare nari mfite muri iki gihe, ampobera ku rutugu, ampereza ikiganza, ambwira ko ejo nziteguye.
"Yiringiye byimazeyo.
Afite umwanya w'icyubahiro mu ruhame kandi yagize uruhare runini mu makipe mu gihe cyashize no muri iki cyumweru.
Wenda ntiyari azi ko yari gukina imikino ibiri.
Natekerezaga ko yari gukina cyane, ariko amaherezo ni uko ibintu bimeze, kandi ni uko twabyumvaga.
Kimwe n'abandi bose, yifuza kuba hanze".
Ku cyumweru, Mickelson azatsinda Nick Faldo ku mwanya wa mbere mu mikino myinshi ya Ryder Cup.
Ashobora kuba yarangije isiganwa rye rya Ryder Cup, isiganwa ritigeze rigera ku rwego rw'ibaruramari rye.
