Ubwato bushya bw'intambara bw'Ubudage bwagombaga gutangwa mu 2014, busimbura ubwato bw'intambara bwa kera bwo mu gihe cy'intambara y'ubutita, ariko ntibuzageza nibura mu mwaka utaha kubera imikorere mibi n'igiciro gihanitse, bitangajwe n'ibinyamakuru byo muri ako gace.
