Biteganyijwe ko bazahabwa imbunda ikomeye, ibisasu bitandukanye byo kurwanya indege n'amato, ndetse n'ikoranabuhanga ryo guhisha, nka radar igabanutse, infra-rouge n'amajwi.
Ibindi bintu byingenzi birimo igihe kirekire cyo kubungabunga, bigomba kuba bishoboka kohereza ibyuma bishya kugeza kumyaka ibiri hanze y'ibyambu by'inkomoko.
Ariko kandi, nk'uko ikinyamakuru cyitwa Die Zeit kibivuga, uko gutinda gutinda byatumaga amato y'intambara afite ikoranabuhanga rigezweho, kandi yatumaga Ubudage bushobora kwereka ibihugu imbaraga zabwo mu mahanga, aba asa n'ayatakaye igihe yari kuba atangiye gukora.
Iyi ndege y'intambara F125 y'amahirwe make, yabaye inkuru mu mwaka ushize ubwo ingabo z'Abadage zanze ku mugaragaro ko iyo ndege ya gisirikare y'intambara igomba gutangira imirimo, maze bayisubiza mu bwubatsi bw'i Hamburg, mu kigo cya Blohm & Voss.
Bwari ubwa mbere ingabo z'inyanja z'Amerika zisubiza ubwato abubaka nyuma yo kubutanga.
Nta byinshi byari bizwi ku mpamvu zatumye iki cyambu gisubira inyuma, ariko itangazamakuru ry'Abadage ryavuze ku "byaha bikomeye mu ikoranabuhanga no mu bikoresho" byatumye iki cyambu kidashobora gukoreshwa mu bikorwa by'intambara.
Ibikosa bya porogaramu byari bikomeye cyane, kuko ubwato bwa Baden-Wuerttemberg buzakoreshwa n'abakozi 120; ni ukuvuga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abakozi basabwa kuri feriyatsi ya kera ya Bremen.
Byongeye kandi, ubwato bwasanze burengeje cyane, byangiza imikorere yabwo kandi bigabanya ubushobozi bwingabo zirwanira mu mazi bwo kongeramo ivugurura mu gihe kiri imbere.
Ubwato bwa Rheinland-Pfalz bw'itoni ibihumbi birindwi, buterwa amabuye inshuro ebyiri z'ubwato bw'ubwoko bumwe bwakoreshejwe n'Abadage mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi yose.
Uretse ibyuma bidafite ubuziranenge, igiciro rusange cyumushinga, ikubiyemo amahugurwa y'abakozi, nayo iri guhinduka ikibazo.
Bivugwa ko ubu imaze kugera ku mafaranga atavugwa angana na miriyari 3100 z'ama euro, mu gihe yari miliyari 2200 yari iteganyijwe.
Ikibazo cy'amato mashya y'intambara gifite agaciro gakomeye cyane cyane mu gihe hari ibimenyetso biheruka ko ubwato bw'u Budage burimo gusenyuka.
Mu ntangiriro z'uyu mwaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, umuyobozi w'inteko ishinga amategeko y'ingabo mu nteko ishinga amategeko y'u Budage, yemeye ko ingabo z'ingabo z'u Budage zitagira amato yo gukoresha.
Uyu muyobozi avuga ko iki kibazo cy'ubushomeri kigenda cyiyongera, kubera ko amato ashaje yagiye akurwaho ariko nta yandi asimbuye.
Nanone kandi, yababajwe n'uko nta na rimwe mu mato y'ubwoko bwa Baden-Wuerttemberg rigeze rihabwa ububasha bwo kujya mu ngabo z'Amerika.
National Trust irigenga ku buzima bw'amavunja
Ubushakashatsi bushya burimo gukorwa mu isambu yo mu misozi ya Scotland, bugamije kugaragaza uko injangwe zikoresha isambu mu gushakisha ibyokurya.
Biteganyijwe ko ibyagezweho bizatuma turushaho gusobanukirwa imyitwarire y'izo nyamaswa z'inyamaswa ziguruka kandi bigatuma n'ibikorwa byo kuzitaho birushaho gukorwa.
Ubu bushakashatsi buyobowe n'abahanga bo mu kigo cy'igihugu cy'ubushakashatsi ku by'ibidukikije cya Scotland (National Trust for Scotland) buzakurikirana udusimba twa Pipistrellus pygmaeus na Pipistrellus pipistrellus, ndetse n'udusimba twa Myotis daubentonii na Plecotus auritus mu busitani bwa Inverewe muri Wester Ross.
Ibikoresho byihariye byo gufata amajwi bizashyirwa ahantu hakomeye hafi y'umutungo kugirango ukurikirane ibikorwa by'ibicurane mugihe cy'umwaka.
Abakozi ba NHS n'abakorerabushake nabo bazakora ubushakashatsi kuri telefone bakoresheje ibikoresho byo mu ntoki.
Abahanga mu gusesengura amajwi bazareba incuro izo nguge zihamagara n'uko buri bwoko buzivuga.
Nyuma y'aho, bazashyiraho ikarita y'aho batuye kugira ngo bagire isura isobanutse y'imiterere y'ubwoko bwabo.
Rob Dewar, umujyanama mu by'ibidukikije muri NTS, yizeye ko ibisubizo bizagaragaza uturere tw'aho tuzwi cyane ku ducurama n'uko dukoreshwa n'amoko atandukanye.
Aya makuru azafasha kumenya inyungu zo gucunga aho hantu, nko mu ishyamba, n'uburyo bwiza bwo kubungabunga amashyamba ku bw'imishwi n'ibindi biremwa bifitanye isano.
Umubare w'inkoramaraso muri Scotland no mu Bwongereza hose wagabanutse cyane mu kinyejana gishize.
Izo nyamaswa zigeramiwe n'ibikorwa by'ubwubatsi n'iterambere bibangamiye ibyarizo n'ibinyabuzima.
Inganda zikoresha umuyaga n'iz'ibiti by'ibiti na zo zishobora guteza akaga, kimwe n'ibigo by'inzige, imiti imwe n'imwe ikoreshwa mu kubaka, n'ibitero by'injangwe.
Bavuga ko ari imishwi, ko ari ibicucu.
Ariko kubera ko izo nyamaswa zihiga nijoro, amatwi yazo ni yo akenewe cyane mu gihe zihiga kurusha amaso yazo.
Bakoresha uburyo buhambaye bwo kumenya aho udukoko n'ibindi bintu bibagora biri mu nzira y'urugendo.
NTS, ifite inshingano zo kwita ku nyubako z'amateka zirenga 270, ubusitani 38 n'ubutaka bwa hegitari 76 000 mu gihugu hose, ifata ingona cyane.
Ifite impuguke 10 zigiye, kandi buri gihe zisohoza ubushakashatsi, zigenzura ibyana, ndetse rimwe na rimwe zigakora ibikorwa byo gutabara.
Iryo shyirahamwe rifite n'ikigega kimwe rukumbi cya mbere cya Scotland bat muri Threave Estate muri Dumfries na Galloway, kikaba ari icumbi ry'amoko umunani ku icumi y'inguge zo muri Scotland.
David Thompson, ushinzwe ibijyanye n'umutungo w'igihugu, avuga ko iki ari igihugu cyiza kuri bo.
Yagize ati "mu mujyi wa Threave dufite ahantu hanini ho kurara injangwe.
"Dufite inyubako za kera, ibiti by'amateka n'ibidukikije byiza.
Ariko hari byinshi tutaramenya kuri utwo ducurama, bityo, umurimo dukora hano no ku bindi bihingwa uzadufasha kurushaho gusobanukirwa ibyo dukeneye kugira ngo dutunge imibereho myiza".
Ashimangira akamaro ko kugenzura imiterere y'amavunja mbere yo gukora imirimo yo kubungabunga umutungo, kuko bishoboka ko kurimbura kw'amavunja rimwe ry'ababyeyi bishobora kwica abagore n'abana 400, ibyo bikaba byashobora kurimbura abaturage bose.
Ni mu gihe kandi n'abategetsi b'u Rwanda bari mu bikorwa byo kurwanya iyo ndwara.
Elisabeth Ferrell, umutegetsi wo muri Ecosse w'umuryango bat Conservation Trust, ashishikariza abantu gufasha:
Ati "Haracyari byinshi byo kumenya ku ducurama, kandi ku moko menshi y'izo ducurama, ntituzi uko zimeze".
Ronaldo yanze ibirego byo gusambanya abagore ku ngufu, kandi abamwunganira bitegura kuburana n'ikinyamakuru cyo mu Budage
Cristiano Ronaldo avuga ko ibirego byo gusambanywa ku gahato bimugezeho ari ibinyoma, avuga ko icyo abantu bifuza ari ukwiyerekana bakoresheje izina rye.
Abunganira Bwana Trump mu mategeko bazamurega ikinyamakuru cyo mu Budage Der Spiegel kubera ko cyatangaje ibyo birego.
Uyu rutahizamu w'ikipe ya Portugal na Juventus, ashinjwa gufata ku ngufu Kathryn Mayorga, Umunyamerika, muri hoteli i Las Vegas mu 2009.
Uyu mukinnyi w'umupira w'amaguru bivugwa ko yishyuye uyu mugore amadolari 375.000 kugira ngo atagira icyo avuga kuri iki kibazo, nkuko Der Spiegel yabitangaje ku wa Gatanu.
Nyuma y'amasaha make iyi nkuru itangajwe, Ronaldo w'imyaka 33 yavuguruje aya makuru mu buryo bw'amashusho ya videwo kuri konti ye ya Instagram, ikurikirwa n'abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 142.
"Oya, oya, kandi incuro igihumbi, oya.
Ibyo twavuze uyu munsi ni ibinyoma", niko uyu mukinnyi watsindiye Ballon d'Or inshuro eshanu yavuze imbere y'abari aho.
"Abantu bifuza kumenyekana bakoresheje izina ryanjye.
Ni ibisanzwe.
bashaka kumenyekana bavuga izina ryanjye, ni kimwe mu bigize akazi kanjye.
Ndi umugabo wishimye kandi wubahwa", umukinnyi yongeyeho amwenyura.
Abunganira Ronaldo bitegura kujuririra ikinyamakuru Der Spiegel ku birego by'urubuga rwacyo, Reuters ivuga ko ari "inyandiko idakwiriye y'ukekwaho ibyaha mu bijyanye n'ubuzima bwite".
Umwunganizi Christian Schertz yavuze ko umukinnyi azasaba indishyi z'akababaro "ku mafaranga angana n'uburemere bw'icyaha, gishobora kuba kimwe mu byaha bikomeye by'uburenganzira bw'umuntu mu myaka ishize".
Iki gitero cyabaye muri Kamena 2019, mu cyumba cy'uburyamo cya Palm Hotel and Casino mu mujyi wa Las Vegas.
Nyuma yo guhurira mu kabyiniro, Ronaldo na Mayorga basubiye mu cyumba cy'umukinnyi, aho bivugwa ko yamusambanyije ku ngufu, nk'uko byemezwa n'inyandiko zashyikirijwe Urukiko rw'Akarere rwa Clark County muri Nevada.
Mayorga avuga ko Ronaldo, nyuma y'icyo gikorwa, yamwibeshyeho avuga ko ari 99% umugabo, ariko ko uwo 1% yamugambaniye.
Inyandiko zivuga ko Ronaldo yemeje ko bombi bakoranye imibonano mpuzabitsina ku bushake bw'impande zombi.
Mayorga kandi avuga ko yagiye kuri polisi kandi ko yari afite amafoto y'ibikomere, ariko nyuma yemera kuburana mu buryo butunguranye kubera ko yari afite ubwoba bw'ibihano kandi ahangayikishijwe no gutukwa n'abaturage.
Uyu mugore w'imyaka 34 avuga ko ashaka gusesa amasezerano y'ubukwe mu gihe akomeje kubabazwa n'ibyabaye.
Mu gihe cy'icyaha cy'ihohoterwa, Ronaldo yari agiye guhura na Real Madrid avuye muri Manchester United, kandi muri iyi mpeshyi yinjiye mu ikipe y'Itorero rikomeye ry'Ubutaliyani Juve mu masezerano ya miliyoni 100 z'amayero.
Brexit: Inganda z'imodoka zigiye kuva mu Bwongereza
Ubwongereza buzahora bwicuza ko buzahomba umwanya wabwo nk'icyicaro cy'isi mu gukora imodoka nyuma ya Brexit, nkuko umunyamabanga w'ubucuruzi Greg Clark yabitangaje.
Yongeyeho ko biteye impungenge kuba Toyota UK yarivugiye kuri BBC ko mu gihe Ubwongereza bwava muri EU nta masezerano bagiranye, izatuma iherezo ry'ibikorwa byayo mu ruganda rwa Burnaston, ruri hafi ya Derby, rihagarara by'agateganyo.
"Ni ngombwa ko tugirana amasezerano", Clark yongeyeho.
Uruganda rukora imodoka rwo mu Buyapani rwatangaje ko mu gihe Brexit yaba nta masezerano agaragaye, ingaruka z'ihagarikwa ry'imirimo ku mupaka zishobora gutwara abantu akazi.
Uruganda rwa Burnaston rukora modoka za Toyota Auris na Avensis, rwakoze imodoka zigera ku 150.000 mu mwaka ushize, 90% z'izo modoka zoherejwe mu bindi bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi.
Marvin Cooke, umuyobozi mukuru wa Toyota i Burnaston yagize ati "Mu bitekerezo byanjye, niba Ubwongereza buvuye mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, tuzabona umusaruro uhagaze mu ruganda rwacu".
Abandi bakora imodoka mu Bwongereza nabo bagaragaje ubwoba bwo kuva muri EU nta masezerano bagiranye ku bijyanye no gukora ubucuruzi bwambukiranya imipaka, barimo Honda, BMW na Jaguar Land Rover.
Urugero, BMW yemeje ko izfunga uruganda rwayo rwa Mini mu mujyi wa Oxford ukwezi kumwe nyuma ya Brexit.
Kimwe mu bintu bihangayikishije cyane abakora imodoka ni ibyago byo gutakaza isoko mu gihe Brexit yaba itaremeranyijweho.
Urwego rw'ibikoresho bya Toyota ni ruto cyane, buri minota 37 haza ibice bivuye mu Bwongereza no mu muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi bitanga imodoka z'akataraboneka.
Niba ku wa 29 Werurwe Ubwongereza buvuye mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi budafite amasezerano, umupaka ushobora guhungabana, kandi hashobora kuvuka ikibazo cy'ibikoresho bidashobora kuboneka.
Iyi sosiyete ivuga ko bitashoboka ko Toyota yagumana umuvuduko usanzwe umunsi umwe mu ruganda rwa Derbyshire, bityo umusaruro ugomba guhagarara.
Clark avuga ko gahunda ya Theresa May ya Chequers ku mubano w'ejo hazaza n'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi "yashyizwe mu buryo bwitondewe kugira ngo hakumirwe ibyo byitwa ko ari igenzura ku mupaka".
"Ni ngombwa kugira amasezerano. Kandi turashaka ko aba meza, kugira ngo tubashe kwishimira intsinzi dufite ubu ariko tunagire amahirwe menshi muri aya masezerano", ni ko yavuze mu kiganiro Today cya BBC Radio 4.
"Ubumenyi bwa Toyota n'abandi bakora ni uko ari ngombwa gukomeza ubu bucuruzi bwiza".
Toyota ntiyashoboye kumenya igihe inganda zizamara zidakora, ariko yaburiye ko mu gihe kirekire, ibiciro byiyongereye bizatuma uruganda ruguca intege kandi bishobora no gutwara akazi.
Peter Tsouvallaris, umukozi wa Burnaston mu myaka 24 akaba n'umuhuzabikorwa w'ishyirahamwe Unite, yavuze ko abanyamuryango babo bagenda barushaho guhangayika: "Niboneye ko iyo ibyo bikorwa byamaze kugenda, ntibisubira.
Umuvugizi wa guverinoma yavuze ko batanze gahunda igaragara kandi y'ukuri ku mibanire y'igihe kizaza hagati y'u Bwongereza na EU.
Inama ya Trump na Rosenstein ishobora kongera gusubikwa
Ibiro bya perezida wa Amerika, White House, byavuze ko inama y'ibanga ya Donald Trump na Minisitiri w'Ubutabera w'Amerika, Rosenstein ishobora gusubikwa indi cyumweru kubera impaka z'umukandida mu rukiko rw'ikirenga, Brett Kavanaugh.
Rosenstein agenzura ibikorwa by'umwunganizi wihariye Robert Mueller, uri gukora iperereza ku kwivanga kw'Uburusiya mu matora, imikoranire hagati y'abashyigikiye Uburusiya na Trump, n'ubutabera bushobora gukomwa mu nkokora na perezida.
Yaba Trump yirukanye umushinjacyaha mukuru wungirije cyangwa se ataramwirukana, ibyo bikaba byashyira mu kaga ubwigenge bwa Mueller, byateje impaka muri Washington mu gihe cy'amezi menshi.
Mu ntangiriro y'uku kwezi, ikinyamakuru The New York Times cyatangaje ko Rosenstein yavuze ko yakoresha mikoro mu kuganira na Trump ndetse ko ashobora no gukura Perezida ku butegetsi hakoreshejwe Amendement ya 25.
Icyakora, Rosenstein yahakanye ibyo yari yavuze.
Ariko ku wa mbere w'icyumweru gishize yagiye muri White House, mu gihe hari amakuru avuga ko ari hafi kwegura ku mirimo ye.
Ahubwo, habaye inama na Trump, wari i New York ku wa kane.
Trump yavuze ko yifuzaga kutirukana Rosenstein, ariko inama yatinze kugira ngo yirinde kugongana n'inama y'inama y'abadepite y'urukiko yitabiriye Kavanaugh na Christine Blasey Ford, umwe mu bagore bashinja Trump imyitwarire idahwitse mu by'imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ku wa Gatanu, Trump yategetse ko FBI ikora iperereza ry'icyumweru kimwe ku birego bya Kavanaugh, bituma itinda amatora ya Sena kurushaho.
Sarah Sanders, umunyamabanga wa Trump, yagaragaye kuri Fox News Sunday.
Abajijwe ku itariki azabonera Rosenstein, yagize ati "Nta tariki iracyagena, ishobora kuba muri iki cyumweru cyangwa se ikagena ikindi cyumweru, bitewe n'ibyabaye mu rukiko rw'ikirenga.
Tuzareba, ariko, uzi ko nkunda ko itangazamakuru rihabwa amakuru".
Bamwe mu banyamakuru bahakanye ibyo, kuko Sanders amaze iminsi adafite ikiganiro n'abanyamakuru kuva ku ya 10 Nzeri.
Ubwo Chris Wallace wari umuhagarariye yamubazaga impamvu,
Sanders yavuze ko kuba nta biganiro by'amakuru byatangiwe atari ukubera kwanga ubuhanga bw'abanyamakuru, nubwo yongeyeho ko atari we uzamuhakana.
Yongeyeho ko Trump azakomeza guhura n'abanyamakuru.
"Perezida atanga ibiganiro byinshi kurusha perezida wa mbere", yatangaje, nubwo nta soko yatanze yo gushyigikira ayo makuru.
Sanders yavuze ko ibiganiro bizakomeza, ariko ashimangira ko "iyo itangazamakuru rihawe amahirwe yo kubaza Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, byaba byiza cyane kurusha kumubaza ibibazo.
Muri abahamya b'ukuntu twagiye dukora ibi mu byumweru bike bishize, kandi bizasimbura ikiganiro n'abanyamakuru aho ushobora kuvugana na perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika".
Trump akunze gusubiza ibibazo iyo avuye muri White House cyangwa yitabiriye ibiganiro byuguruye cyangwa inama z'abanyamakuru n'abashyitsi bakuru.
