Abaguzi b'abanyamahanga bazishyurwa umusoro w'inyongera ku biciro by'inzu igihe bazaba bagura ibintu mu Bwongereza. Theresa May azatangaza ko ayo mafaranga y'inyongera azakoreshwa mu gufasha abatagira aho baba.
Iyi ngingo izafatwa nk'igamije guhangana n'ibikorwa bya Jeremy Corbyn byo kwiba amajwi y'urubyiruko mu masezerano yo guteza imbere inzu zifite ubushobozi bwo kugenerwa n'abantu benshi no kwibanda ku bantu bafite amafaranga menshi.
Umusoro uzongerwa ku mpapuro z'itumanaho uzashyirwa ku bantu n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi bidatanga umusoro mu Bwongereza, kandi amafaranga azakoreshwa mu gushyigikira gahunda ya Leta yo kugabanya umubare w'abantu barara ku muhanda.
Ikiguzi cyo hejuru, cyiyongereye ku misoro y'ibiro iriho ubu, harimo n'ibiciro biri hejuru byashyizweho mu myaka ibiri ishize ku nzu z'ubucuruzi no kugura ibintu bicuruzwa, bishobora kuba 3%.
Ubutegetsi bw'igihugu buvuga ko butegereje ko icyo gikorwa cy'ihinduka kizatuma haboneka amafaranga agera kuri miriyoni 120 z'amapawundi ku mwaka.
Hafi ya 13% by'inyubako nshya zubatswe i Londres zigurwa n'abatari abatuye mu Bwongereza, ibyo bikaba birimo gutuma ibiciro byiyongera kandi bigatuma abantu bashaka kugura inzu bwa mbere bagira ingorane zo kwinjira mu isoko ry'imitungo.
Ibice byinshi bikize by'igihugu, cyane cyane mu murwa mukuru, byahindutse "imidugudu y'imyuka" kubera umubare munini w'abaguzi b'abanyamahanga bamara igihe kinini hanze y'igihugu.
Iyi politiki nshya yashyizwe mu bikorwa hashize ibyumweru bike Boris Johnson asabye ko hasinywa ku misoro yo kwimurira imitungo kugira ngo abantu bashya bafashwe kugura inzu yabo ya mbere.
Yashinje ibigo bikomeye by'ubwubatsi ko bigumisha ibiciro by'inzu hejuru binyuze mu kugura ubutaka no kubukoresha, kandi asaba Madamu May gukuraho imisanzu y'imisoro ku ngo z'amazu y'igiciro cyo hagati kugira ngo akemure "isoni z'ubwubatsi" mu Bwongereza.
Bwana Corbyn yatangaje ibintu bishishikaje by'ivugurura ry'inzu, harimo no kugenzura abakodesha bakodesha ndetse no guca amazu abuza abayatuyemo.
Ashaka kandi guha abayobozi b'uturere ububasha bukomeye mu gihe cyo kubaka amazu mashya.
May yagize ati "Mu mwaka ushize navuze ko nari kwegurira manda yanjye kugarura inzozi z'Abongereza: ko ubuzima bwagombye kuba bwiza kuri buri gisekuru gishya.
Kugira ngo ibyo bishoboke, hakenewe ko habaho gahunda yo gukemura ikibazo cy'ubukene bw'imitungo.
Ubwongereza buhora bwiteguye kubw'umuntu wese ushaka gutura, gukora no gutangira ubuzima bwe hano.
Ariko kandi, ntabwo ari byiza ko byoroha ku bantu batuye hanze y'Ubwongereza, kimwe n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi bikorera mu mahanga, kugura amazu kurusha Abongereza bakora.
Kuri benshi, inzozi zo kugira inzu yabo bwite ni inzozi zitagihishurwa, kandi kuba batagira aho kuba, biracyari inzozi nyakuri".
Jack Ross: "Intego yanjye ikomeye ni iyo gutoza Scotland".
Umuyobozi wa Sunderland, Jack Ross, yatangaje ko "intego ye ya nyuma" ari ukuba umukinnyi wa shampiyona ya Scotland igihe runaka.
Uyu mushakashatsi w'imyaka 42 y'amavuko, ari mu byishimo bikomeye byo guhagurukira ikipe yo mu majyaruguru y'uburengerazuba, ubu iri ku mwanya wa gatatu muri League One, ikaba iri ku mwanya wa gatatu.
Yageze ku kibuga cy'umucyo muri iyi mpeshyi nyuma yo gusubiza St Mirren mu cyiciro cya mbere cya Scotland umwaka ushize.
"Nkiri umukinnyi wa baseball, nari mfite inzozi zo gukinira igihugu cyanjye.
Nakinnye rimwe mu ikipe ya B, kandi nibyo byose", Ross yabwiye ikiganiro cya BBC Scotland Sportsound.
"Nakuriye mbona Scotland ikina muri Hampden kenshi na papa nkiri umwana, ikintu nifuzaga kongera kubaho.
Ariko ibyo bizaba ari uko gusa mfite amahirwe yo kuyobora ikipe".
Mu babanjirije Ross mu gihe cy'ubuyobozi bwa Sunderland harimo Dick Advocaat, David Moyes, Sam Allardyce, Martin O'Neill, Roy Keane, Gus Poyet na Paulo Di Canio.
Uwari ushinzwe gucunga Alloa Athletic yemeza ko nta mpungenge yumvaga zo kurongora abo bantu bakomeye cyane muri iyi kipe ikomeye nyuma yo kwanga mbere gusimbura Barnsley na Ipswich Town.
"Ese amahirwe mfite yo gutsinda muri iki gihe azaterwa n'uko nashoboye gusubiza iyi kipe mu cyiciro cya mbere?
Kubera ko imiterere n'ibikoresho by'ikipe by'ikipe nta gushidikanya ko ari iby'ikipe ya Premier League".
"Ntabwo ari igikorwa cyoroshye, ariko nshobora kubona ko ari ikintu cyonyine cyatumye ngera hano niba nshobora gusubiza iyi kipe muri Premier League".
Ross amaze imyaka itatu gusa nk'umutoza nyuma y'igihe yari umufasha wa Dumbarton n'igihe cy'amezi 15 mu bakozi b'abatoza ba Hearts.
Muri icyo gihe yafashije Alloa gukira kuva mu cyiciro cya gatatu no gutuma St Mirren ava mu kuba hafi yo kumanuka akajya mu cyiciro cya gatatu, akabona igikombe cya shampiyona umwaka ukurikiyeho.
Ross avuga ko ubu yumva yisanzuye kurusha uko yigeze mu gihe cyose yamaze akina muri Clyde, Hartlepool, Falkirk, St Mirren na Hamilton Academical.
Yibukije ko igihe yari agiye gufata uwo muyobozi, "ashobora kuba yari agiye kugera ku muhanda uhuza imihanda.
"Mu by'ukuri, natekerezaga ko gutoza byari binkwiriye, ndetse kurusha no gukina.
Birasa nkaho bitangaje kuko nta kibazo nagize, nagize imibereho myiza mu rugero runaka, kandi ngera ku bintu bimwe na bimwe.
Ariko gukina bishobora kugorana.
Hari ibintu byinshi ugomba gusobanukirwa buri cyumweru.
Ndacyafite ibibazo by'umunaniro n'ibihe by'akazi, ariko ndacyakunda imyitozo.
Nakundaga gukora siporo, kandi ubu ko mbikora, numva nisanzuye kurusha ikindi gihe cyose mu buzima bwanjye bwo mu gihe cy'amabyiruka".
Mushobora kumva ikiganiro cyose kuri Sportsound ku cyumweru tariki ya 30 Nzeri kuri Radio Scotland hagati ya 12:00 na 13:00 (igihe cy'imbera mu Bwongereza)
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko isaha nziza yo kunywa inzoga ari saa cyenda n'igice z'umugoroba ku wa Gatandatu
Ubushyuhe bw'impeshyi bwatumye ibinyobwa mu kabari by'u Bwongereza birushaho gukena, ariko byongera imbaraga ku ma hoteli.
Ibitaro n'utubari byagize ukwiyongera kwa 2.7 ku ijana muri Nyakanga, ariko igura mu maresitora ryagabanutseho 4.8 ku ijana nk'uko imibare ibigaragaza.
Peter Martin, umwe mu bagize inama y'ubucuruzi ya CGA, ishinzwe gukusanya imibare, yagize ati "iminsi y'izuba n'igihe kirekire cy'Ubwongereza mu mupira w'amaguru cy'isi cyatumye muri Nyakanga hagaragara imiterere isa n'iya Kamena, aho utubari twishimiye kuzamuka kwa 2.8 ku ijana mu gukoresha, nubwo resitora yahuye n'igihano gikomeye.
Igabanuka rya 1.8% ry'igiciro cy'amafaranga yinjira muri resitora muri Kamena ryarushijeho kuba kibi muri Nyakanga.
Ibirayi n'utubari by'inzoga ni byo byagize umusaruro mwiza cyane mu kwiyongera kw'ibinyobwa birenze kugabanyuka kwagiye kwibonerwa n'amazu yo muri resitora.
Amaduka acuruza ibiryo na yo yahuye n'ingaruka z'izuba, n'ubwo atari cyane nk'uko bimeze ku bagurisha ibiryo.
Abantu basa n'abashakaga kujya mu kabari kunywa inzoga.
Mu tubari tw'inyuma twagenzuwe, kunywa inzoga byazamutseho 6.6 ku ijana mu gihe cy'ukwezi, naho kurya byagabanutseho 3 ku ijana".
Paul Newman, umukozi w'ikigo RSM gishinzwe gusesengura ibikorwa by'imyidagaduro n'ubukerarugendo, yagize ati "Ibi bivuze ko hagendewe ku buryo byagiye bigenda kuva mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa kane.
Igihe n'ingaruka z'ibirori bikomeye by'imibereho n'imikino bikomeje kuba ibintu by'ingenzi mu bijyanye n'ibikoreshwa hanze y'inzu.
Ntibitangaje kuba amashyirahamwe y'amafunguro akomeje guhura n'ibibazo, ariko igihombo cya 4.8% ku mwaka kizababaza cyane cyane niba ibyo bihujwe no kwiyongera kw'ibiciro.
Igihe cy'impeshyi kirekire kandi gishyushye nticyari igihe kibi cyane ku bucuruzi bwo muri resitora, kandi igihe ni cyo kizatubwira niba ubushyuhe bushyuha bwo muri Kanama buzatanga ubufasha bukenewe cyane muri uyu mwuga".
Ibyagurishijwe byose mu tubari n'amaresitora, harimo n'ibyafunguwe, byariyongereyeho 2.7% muri Nyakanga, bikaba bigaragaza ko ibikorwa byo gushyira ku mugaragaro ibidandazwa by'amazina y'ubucuruzi byagabanutse.
Ikigereranyo cy'ibicuruzwa by'inganda za Coffer Peach Tracker Industry mu nganda zikora inzo n'amafunguro mu Bwongereza gikusanya kandi kigasuzuma imibare ku musaruro w'amatsinda 47 y'ibikorwa hamwe n'inyungu z'umurengera zisaga miliyari 9 z'amapawundi kandi ifatwa nk'aho ari yo ntambwe y'urwego rw'urwego.
Umwana umwe muri batanu afite konti y'ibanga yo ku mbuga nkoranyambaga ababyeyi babo batazi
Iperereza ryakozwe ku bana bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 11 gusa, ryagaragaje ko umwe muri batanu afite konti yihariye yo kuri interineti ababyeyi n'abarimu batamenya
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku banyeshuri 20,000 bo mu mashuri yisumbuye bwagaragaje ko umubare w'imbuga za Instagram z'impimbano wazamutse
Iyi nkuru yatumye abantu batinya ko inyandiko zerekeranye n'ubusambanyi zishobora kujya ku mbuga nkoranyambaga.
20% by'abanyeshuri bavuze ko bafite konti y'umukuru wabo kugira ngo bajye bayereka ababyeyi babo
Umwana umwe kuri batanu (bamwe bafite imyaka 11 gusa) barimo barashinga konti ku mbuga nkoranyambaga z'abantu bakuru.
Iperereza ryakozwe ku banyeshuri bo mu mashuri yisumbuye bagera ku 20.000 ryagaragaje ko umubare w'abantu bakoresha urubuga rwa Instagram rwamamaza amafoto y'abantu benshi, wariyongereye cyane.
Iyi nkuru yatumye abantu batinya ko inyandiko z'urukozasoni zishobora gusohoka.
20% by'abanyeshuri bavuze ko bakoresha konti "y'ibanze" yoroheje kugira ngo bereke ababyeyi babo ko bafite konti bwite.
Umubyeyi wabonye konti y'umukobwa we w'imyaka 13 yihishe, yahuye n'umukobwa w'ingimbi wasabaga ko "bazamusambanya".
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Digital Awareness UK n'ihuriro ry'abayobozi b'amashuri yigenga (HMC), bwasanze 40% by'abana bari hagati y'imyaka 11 na 18 bafite imyirondoro ibiri, kandi kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bemeye ko bafite konti zabo bwite.
Mike Buchanan, umuyobozi wa HMC, yagize ati "biratangaje kubona abakiri bato benshi cyane bagerageza gukora imbuga nkoranyambaga ababyeyi n'abarimu badashobora kubona".
Eilidh Doyle azaba "ijwi ry'abakinnyi" mu nama y'ishyirahamwe ry'imikino ngororangingo ryo muri Ecosse
Eilidh Doyle yatoranijwe mu nama y'ishyirahamwe ry'imikino ngororamubiri muri Ecosse nk'umuyobozi udafite inshingano mu nama rusange y'umwaka y'inama y'ubuyobozi.
Doyle niwe mukinnyi wa Scottish wahawe ibihembo byinshi kandi umuyobozi Ian Beattie yavuze ko iki cyemezo ari amahirwe akomeye ku bayobozi b'imikino bungukirwa n'ubunararibonye bwabo ku rwego mpuzamahanga mu myaka icumi ishize.
Beattie yagize ati: "Eilidh yubahwa cyane mu baturage ba Scotland, mu Bwongereza no ku isi hose, kandi twizeye ko siporo yo muri Scotland izungukirwa cyane no kuba ari mu nama".
Doyle yagize ati: "Nifuza cyane kuba umuvugizi w'abakinnyi kandi nizeye ko nzagira uruhare kandi mfashe kuyobora siporo muri Ecosse".
Umunyamerika, wegukanye metero 200 na metero 400 mu mikino yo muri Atlanta 1996 mu batsindiye imyanya ine ya Olempike kandi ubu akora nk'umunyamakuru w'igihe cyose kuri BBC, yagize ikibazo cy'indwara ya ischemic y'akanya gato imubuza kugenda.
Yanditse kuri Twitter ati "Mu kwezi gushize nagize ikibazo cyo mu bwonko.
Ntiyashoboraga kugenda.
Abaganga bavuze ko igihe ari cyo cyari gutuma menya niba nzakira, n'aho nzagera.
Byari akazi gakomeye, ariko nabashije gukira neza, nongera kwiga kugenda kandi ubu nkora imyitozo yo guhumeka.
Ndabashimira ku bw'ubutumwa bwanyu buhumuriza"
Itangazo ry'ikigo cy'ubucuruzi gikoresha amazi mu kubyaza abana, rigereranya abagore n'inka, ryacamo ibice ibitekerezo by'abaturage kuri interineti
Ikigo kimwe gikora ibikoresho by'ibere cyateye urujijo mu baturage binyuze mu kwamamaza ikiganiro cy'ikinyamakuru cy'itangazamakuru aho cyashushanyaga abagore batwite inka n'inka zisigaye.
Mu gutangaza ko hagiye gushyirwaho "umuti w'amata w'ifu utanyurwamo mu isi", ikigo Elvie cyasohoye itangazo ry'urwenya mu buryo bw'amashusho y'indirimbo igaragaza umudendezo umuheheha w'ababyeyi.
Abagore bane b'ibwami babyina mu kiraro cyuzuye ibyatsi by'inka, ku buryo indirimbo ifite amagambo nk'aya ngo "Yego, ndiyicira ariko nta n'umurizo mfite" na "Niba utari ubizi, si amabere yanjye, ni amabere yanjye".
Iyo korari ikomeza igira iti "Mug, mug, mugg, I'm feeding babies, mug, mug, I'm mugging my friends".
Icyakora, itangazo ryashyizwe ku rubuga rwa Facebook rw'iyi kompanyi, ryateje impaka ku mbuga nkoranyambaga.
Nyuma yo kurebwa inshuro zigera ku 77.000 no gusubirwamo inshuro amagana, iyi video yatumye abantu bitabira mu buryo butandukanye, benshi bavuga ko igaragaza "amahano" agaragara mu buhinzi bw'amata.
"Gukoresha inka mu kwamamaza iki gikoresho byari ibyemezo bigayitse.
Nk'uko natwe dukenera gutwita no kubyara kugira ngo dutange amata, ariko mu gihe cyabo twibye abana babo nyuma y'iminsi mike babyaye".
Igikoresho cyo gukoramo amata cya Elvie gishobora gushyirwa mu buryo bw'ibanga mu gikoresho cy'umubyeyi (Elvie/nai)
Undi mubyitegereza yagize ati "byumvikana ko ari ibikomere ku mubyeyi n'umwana.
Ariko se koko, kuki batakoreshwa mu kwamamaza ikimasa cy'amata ku babyeyi bagumana n'abana babo?"
Undi muntu wari aho yariyamiriye ati "ibyo byatangajwe n'abantu batagira icyo bitaho".
Abandi barebye iyi filime bakomeje kuvuganira iri tangazo, ndetse hari n'umugore umwe wavuze ko iyi ndirimbo "yishekeje cyane".
"Numva ari igitekerezo cyiza.
Niba nari ngifite umutima wo kugura, nari kugura.
Kumwa amata byatumye numva meze nk'inka.
Iri tangazo ry'ikinyamakuru ni irya kinyamwuga, ariko ndumva ari urwenya.
Hari umuntu wanditse ati "nshimishwa n'ibyo mushobora gukora.
Undi yagize ati "Iyi ni itangazo rishimishije rigenewe ababyeyi b'abagore bakura amata yabo (akenshi mu kazi kabo cyangwa mu bwiherero) bakumva bameze nk'inka.
Iri si itangazo ryo gushimira cyangwa gucira urubanza inganda z'amata".
Mu mpera z'iyi video, iri tsinda ry'abagore ryagaragaje ko bari barimo kubyina bakoresheje ibyuma bifata amajwi by'amajwi byabitswe mu bikoresho byabo.
Igitekerezo cy'iyi kampeni ni uko abagore benshi bakamwa amata bavuga ko bumva bameze nk'inka.
Ariko, igikoresho cyo gukama cyitwa Elvie kiratuza rwose, nta mashini cyangwa imijyana, kandi gishobora gushyirwa mu gikoresho cyo gukama cy'umubyeyi, bigatuma abagore bagira umudendezo wo kugendagenda, bakagendana n'abana babo, ndetse no kugendagenda igihe barimo gukama.
Ana Balarin, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe rya Mother yagize ati "Elvie extractor ni igicuruzwa cy'umwimerere gikwiye gutangirwa mu buryo butinyitse kandi bushotora.
Mu gusobanura isano iri hagati y'abagore n'inka z'amata, twifuje kwibanda ku gukama amata n'ibibazo byose biyirimo, ari na ko tugaragaza mu buryo bushimishije kandi bw'igishyika, uburyo bushimishije bwo kumva ko ufite umudendezo utangaje uzaturuka ku gikoresho gishya cy'amata.
Si ubwa mbere Elvie w'umurobyi avugwa cyane mu binyamakuru.
Mu cyumweru cy'imideli cy'i Londres, umubyeyi w'abana babiri yagaragarije umunyabugeni witwa Marta Jakubowski ubwo yakoreshaga iyi myenda.
Abana b'abimukira babarirwa mu magana bahungiye mu nkambi y'impunzi mu gihugu cya Texas
Umubare w'abana b'abimukira bafunzwe wariyongereye nubwo umubare w'abajya ku mupaka buri kwezi wari uhari ugereranyije, ahanini bitewe n'imvugo zikomeye na politiki zashyizweho n'ubutegetsi bwa Trump zagize ingaruka ku gushyirwaho kwa baherwe.
Ubusanzwe, ababyeyi b'abagabo benshi na bo babaga ari abimukira badafite ibyangombwa, kandi batinyaga gushyira mu kaga uburenganzira bwabo bwo kuguma mu gihugu, binyuriye mu gufata iya mbere mu gushaka umwana.
Icyo kibazo cy'umutekano cyarushijeho gukomera muri Kamena, ubwo abayobozi ba leta batangazaga ko abantu bashobora kuba ari ababyeyi b'abashakanye cyangwa abandi bantu bakuze bo mu miryango yabo bagomba gutanga ibimenyetso byabo by'intoki, kandi ko ibyo bisobanuro byari kuzajya bitangwa n'abashinzwe abinjira n'abasohoka.
Mu cyumweru gishize, Matthew Albence, ushinzwe umutekano w'abimukira muri Amerika, yahamije imbere y'inteko ishingamategeko ko ikigo cyabo cyafashe abantu babarirwa mu magana basabye kurera abana batagira ababyeyi.
Nyuma y'aho, ibiro by'iperereza byemeje ko 70% by'abari bafashwe nta manza bari barigeze baregwamo.
"Abagera kuri 80 ku ijana by'abantu bashakanye n'abandi cyangwa abo babana n'abo bashakanye, baba bari muri icyo gihugu mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko, kandi abenshi muri bo ni abanyamahanga bakoze ibyaha.
Ku bw'ibyo, tuzakomeza gukurikirana abo bantu".
Mu rwego rwo kwihutisha imanza z'abana, abayobozi bashyizeho amategeko mashya asaba ko abana bagomba kujya mu rukiko mu gihe kitarenze ukwezi nyuma yo gufatwa, aho kuba iminsi 60 nk'uko byari bisanzwe, nk'uko byemejwe n'abakozi bo muri icyo kigo.
Abenshi bazaza mu buryo bwa videwo aho kuza mu buryo bwa bwite kugira ngo barebe niba bashobora kuburanira imbere y'umucamanza ushinzwe abinjira n'abasohoka.
Abatabifitiye uburenganzira bazahita birukanwa.
Uko bahamara igihe kirekire, ni ko barushaho kugira ubwoba cyangwa kwiheba, bikaba byatera imyivumbagatanyo cyangwa kugerageza gutoroka, nk'uko abakozi b'ubuhungiro n'amakuru y'urwego byatangajwe mu mezi ashize.
Abavoka bavuze ko ibyo byiyumvo by'ubwoba by'abana byiyongera mu bigo binini nka Tornillo, aho ibimenyetso by'uko umwana arwaye bishobora kwirengagizwa bitewe n'uko umwana ari munini.
Bongeyeho kandi ko kujyana abana mu nkambi utabahaye umwanya uhagije wo kubategura mu byiyumvo cyangwa ngo ubabwire ko uhebuje inshuti zabo bishobora kuba byaratumye benshi bakomeza kugira ibikomere.
Syria irasaba ingabo z'Amerika, Ubufaransa na Turukiya guhita ziva mu gihugu
Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga, Walid al-Moualem, ubwo yagezaga ijambo ku nteko rusange y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, nawe yasabye impunzi z'Abasiriya gutaha, nubwo intambara iri mu mwaka wa munani.
Moualem, akaba ari nawe ufite umwanya w'icyegera cy'umushikiranganji wa mbere, yavuze ko ingabo z'amahanga zari ziri ku butaka bwa Syria mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko, mu rwego rwo kurwanya iterabwoba, kandi ko "zagira icyo zikora mu buryo bufatika".
Yabwiye abari aho ati "mugomba guhita muvaho nta shiti".
Moualem yashimangiye ko "intambara yo kurwanya iterabwoba yamaze hafi kurangira" muri Syria, aho abantu barenga 360,000 bamaze gupfa kuva mu mwaka wa 2011 kandi miliyoni z'abandi bahunga ingo zabo.
Yongeyeho ko Damas izakomeza "kurwana iyo ntambara yera kugeza igihe tuzaba twagenzuye intara zose za Siriya" twirinda imitwe y'iterabwoba n' "inyeshyamba zose z'abanyamahanga zitemewe".
Amerika ifite abasirikare bagera ku 2000 muri Siriya, ahanini bagamije gutoza no gutanga inama ingabo z'Abanya-Kurd n'Abanya-Syria b'Abarabu barwanya Perezida Bashar al-Assad.
U Bufaransa bufite abasirikare barenga 1000 muri iki gihugu cyashegeshwe n'intambara.
Ku kibazo cy'impunzi, Moualem yavuze ko hari ibyangombwa byiza byo gutaha kandi ashinja "bamwe mu bihugu by'iburengerazuba" "gukwirakwiza ubwoba budafite ishingiro" butuma impunzi zitararuka.
Yagize ati "Tugiriye inama umuryango mpuzamahanga n'imiryango y'abagiraneza yo gufasha aba bantu gusubira iwabo".
