Umuhungu w'imfura wa Sarah Palin yatawe muri yombi ashinjwa ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu rugo
Track Palin, umuhungu w'imfura w'uwahoze ari guverineri wa Alaska ndetse akaba yari n'umukandida mu cyimbo cya Visi Perezida Sarah Palin, yatawe muri yombi ashinjwa gushinja icyaha cyo gukubita.
Palin w'imyaka 29 ukomoka i Wasilla muri Alaska, yatawe muri yombi akekwaho icyaha cy'ihohoterwa ryo mu ngo, no kubuza umuntu gutanga ikirego cy'ihohoterwa ryo mu ngo no kwanga ubutegetsi, nk'uko byatangajwe n'ingabo za leta ya Alaska.
Raporo y'igipolisi ivuga ko igihe incuti ye yageragezaga guhamagara polisi ngo imubwire iby'ibyo birego, uwo mupolisi yamutwaye telefoni ye.
Palin aracyafungiwe by'agateganyo muri gereza ya Mat-Su Pretrial Facility ku cyemezo cy'urukiko cy'amadolari 500, nk'uko KTUU yabitangaje.
Yagejejwe imbere y'urukiko ku wa Gatandatu, aho yivuze ko "nta cyaha yakoze kuva icyo gihe", nk'uko byatangajwe n'ubuyobozi bw'urukiko.
Palin ahanganye n'ibyaha bitatu byoroheje byo mu rwego rwa A, bivuze ko ashobora gufungwa umwaka umwe kandi agacibwa amande angana n'ibihumbi 250 by'amadolari.
Yashinjwaga kandi icyaha cyo kwica amategeko, kimwe mu bigize icyaha cya B, gihanishwa igifungo cy'umunsi umwe n'ihazabu y'amadolari 2.000.
Si ubwa mbere Palin aregwa ibyaha.
Mu Ukuboza 2017, yashinjwe gushinja se, Todd Palin.
Nyina, Sarah Palin, yahamagaye polisi kugira ngo itange amakuru y'icyo gitero.
Urubanza rwe ubu ruri mu rukiko rw'abari basanzwe mu gisirikare cya Alaska.
Muri Mutarama 2016, yashinjwe ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo, kubuza umuntu gutanga ikirego cy'ihohoterwa rikorerwa mu ngo, no gutunga imbunda yasinze mu gihe cy'icyo gitero.
Umukobwa w'incuti ye amurega ko yamukubise mu maso.
Sarah Palin yanenzwe n'amatsinda y'abahoze ari abasirikare mu 2016 nyuma yo guhuza imyitwarire y'urugomo n'umuhungu we n'indwara yo guhangayika nyuma yo gukomereka nyuma yo gukorana n'ingabo muri Iraki.
Umutingito na tsunami byibasiye Indoneziya bihitana abantu babarirwa mu magana
Abantu bagera kuri 384 ni bo bamaze gupfa nyuma y'umutingito wibasiye ikirwa cya Celebes muri Indoneziya kuwa Gatanu.
Umutingito wo ku gipimo cya 7,5 wangije amazu abarirwa mu bihumbi.
Amashanyarazi n'itumanaho byabuze, kandi umubare w'abapfuye uragenda wiyongera uko iminsi igenda ihita.
Umutingito wibasiye agace ka Central Sulawesi, mu majyaruguru y'uburasirazuba bw'umurwa mukuru wa Indoneziya, Jakarta.
Videwo z'ibihe by'impanuka z'iyo ndege zagiye zigera ku mbuga nkoranyambaga.
Abantu babarirwa mu magana bari bateraniye mu birori byo ku nkombe z'inyanja mu mujyi wa Palu igihe tsunami yageraga ku nkombe.
Abashinjacyaha ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika barimo gushaka uburyo bwo gukatira igihano cy'urupfu gikunze gukoreshwa cyane ku muntu ukekwaho kugaba ibitero by'iterabwoba i New York
Abashinjacyaha b'i New York barimo kugerageza guha igihano cy'urupfu Sayfullo Saipov, ukekwaho kugaba igitero cy'iterabwoba i New York cyahitanye abantu umunani, igihano kitari cyahawe uyu mujyi kuva mu 1953.
Saipov w'imyaka 30 y'amavuko, bivugwa ko yakoresheje ikamyo yakodeshejwe na Home Depot kugira ngo agirire igitero ku muhanda utwara amagare mu muhanda wa West Side Highway i Lower Manhattan, yica abantu n'amagare bahuraga mu nzira mu kwezi kwa cumi.
Kugira ngo urukiko rube rwemeje igihano cy'urupfu, abashinjacyaha bazaba bagomba kugaragaza ko Saipov "yiyemeje" kwica abantu umunani, kandi ko yabakomerekeje "nkana", nk'uko bigaragara mu itangazo ry'icyifuzo cyo gutanga igihano cy'urupfu ryashyizwe mu Ntara y'Amajyepfo ya New York.
Ibi byaha byombi byombi birimo igihano cy'urupfu nk'uko byemezwa n'ibyangombwa by'urukiko.
Mu byumweru byakurikiye icyo gitero, urukiko rw'igihugu rwashinje Saipov ibyaha 22 harimo umunani byo kwica umuntu mu bufatanye n'agatsiko k'abagizi ba nabi, ibyo bikaba ari ibintu bikunze gukoreshwa n'abacamanza mu manza z'abagizi ba nabi, hamwe n'icyaha cy'urugomo no kwangiza imodoka.
Abashinjacyaha bavuze ko icyo gitero cyasabye "gushyiraho gahunda no gutekereza mbere y'igihe" mu gihe bagaragazaga uburyo Saipov yakoze icyo gitero "mu buryo buteye ubwoba, bw'ubugome kandi bw'akahebwe".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov yateje ibikomere, ibyangiritse n'ibyatakaye imiryango n'inshuti za Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza na Alejandro Damian Pagnucco" nkuko byatangajwe mu itangazo ry'umugambi wo kumushinja.
Batanu muri abo bapfuye ni ba mukerarugendo bakomoka muri Arijantine.
Hashize imyaka icumi Akarere ko mu Majyepfo ya New York katigeze gashyiraho igihano cy'urupfu.
Umunyacyaha Khalid Barnes, yahamijwe icyaha cyo kwica abacuruzi babiri b'ibiyobyabwenge, ariko aza gukatirwa igifungo cya burundu muri Nzeri 2009.
Ubwa nyuma igihano cy'urupfu cyakoreshejwe mu rubanza rw'i New York ni mu 1953, mu rubanza rwa Julius na Ethel Rosenberg, umugabo n'umugore we bari barishwe nyuma yo guhamwa n'icyaha cyo kugambirira gukora ubutasi ku bw'Ubumwe bw'Abasoviyeti mu gihe cy'intambara y'ubutita mu myaka ibiri mbere yaho.
Rosenberg yishwe ku itariki ya 19 Kamena 1953.
Saipov wavukiye muri Uzbekistan, yagaragaje ko aticujije mu minsi no mu mezi yakurikiye icyo gitero nk'uko bigaragara mu nyandiko z'urukiko.
Yabwiye abapolisi ko yumvaga ibyo yakoze ari byiza.
Saipov yabwiye abayobozi ko kugira ngo akore icyo gitero, yahumekewe na videwo za ISIS yarebye kuri telefoni ye nk'uko byashinjwe.
Polisi ivuga ko yasabye ko yabona ibendera rya ISIS mu cyumba cye cyo kwa muganga.
Yemeye ibyaha 22 aregwa.
David Patton, umwe mu banyamategeko ba leta bashinzwe kuregera Saipov, yavuze ko "bababajwe cyane" n'umwanzuro w'ubushinjacyaha.
Patton yagize ati "Twizera ko icyemezo cyo gusaba igihano cy'urupfu aho kwemera igihano cy'igifungo cya burundu nta bushobozi bwo kugisubiramo, bizatuma ibikomere byatewe n'ibi bintu biramba ku bantu bose babirimo".
Abunganira Saipov basabye abashinjacyaha ko batakwifuza igihano cy'urupfu.
Umudepite wo mu ishyaka rya Tory avuga ko Nigel Farage yagombye kuba umuyobozi w'ibiganiro kuri Brexit
Nigel Farage yasezeranyije ko azahuza ingabo z'abantu benshi mu myigaragambyo y'uyu munsi mu nama y'abatoye.
Uwahoze ayobora ishyaka ry'ubwigenge mu Bwongereza yavuze ko abanyapolitiki bagomba "kumva igitutu" cy'abashidikanya ku Bwami bw'u Burayi (igihe umwe mu badepite ba Theresa May ubwe yagaragaje ko agomba kwiha gahunda yo kugirana ibiganiro na EU).
Peter Bone, umudepite usanzwe, yabwiye abari mu myigaragambyo i Birmingham ko Ubwongereza bwaba bwarikuye muri EU mu gihe Farage yaba ari we wari Minisitiri ushinzwe Brexit.
Ariko imbogamizi May ahanganye zo guhuza abari mu ishyaka rye ry'amashyaka atandukanye, yagaragaye ubwo abashaka kuguma muri EU bifatanyije n'abari mu myigaragambyo y'abatavuga rumwe na Brexit mu mujyi wa London.
Minisitiri w'intebe arwana no kubahiriza amasezerano y'umugambi we wa Chequers hagati y'ibitero by'abashyigikiye Brexit, abatavuga rumwe na yo ndetse n'ab'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi.
Abari bafatanyije na we bamusabye gukomeza guhangana no kugerageza kumvikana n'i Buruseli nubwo nta cyo bigeze bamusubiza, kugira ngo bahatize abadepite b'Abanyaburayi n'abashyigikiye ishyaka ry'abakozi guhitamo hagati y'icyerekezo cye n'urujijo.
Bwana Bone yavuze mu nama y'ishyaka rya Leave Means Leave i Solihull ko ashaka gushyira iherezo ku mugambi wa Chequers.
Yatangaje ko byari kuba byiza iyo Farage aza kuba ari we ufata iya mbere mu biganiro n'i Buruseli.
Yagize ati "Iyo aza kuba ari we, ubu tuba turi hanze y'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi".
Depite w'i Wellingborough yongeyeho ati "Nzakomeza guharanira Brexit, ariko tugomba guhagarika gahunda ya Chequers".
Mu kugaragaza ko arwanya EU, yagize ati: "Ntabwo turwana intambara z'isi kugira ngo tube imbata.
Turashaka gushyiraho amategeko yacu mu gihugu cyacu.
Bwana Bone yahakanye ibitekerezo byerekana ko ibitekerezo bya rubanda byahindutse kuva amatora yo mu 2016: "Igitekerezo cy'uko abaturage b'Ubwongereza bahinduye ibitekerezo kandi bashaka kuguma muri EU ni ikinyoma rwose".
Umunyapolitiki wo mu ishyaka rya Tory kandi ushyigikiye ko igihugu kiva mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Andrea Jenkyns, nawe yitabiriye iyo myigaragambyo, aho yabwiye abanyamakuru ati: "Icyo navuga gusa ni uko Minisitiri w'Intebe, umva abaturage.
Gahunda ya Chequers ntishimirwa n'abaturage, abatavuga rumwe na leta ntibazayishyigikiye, ntabwo ishyaka ryacu ririkunda ndetse n'abari mu bikorwa by'ubutegetsi, ari bo ba mbere batwaye imihanda kandi batwemerera gutorwa.
Jya uhagarika ibyo Chequers yateganyaga, maze utangire utege amatwi.
Mu butumwa yandikiye Madamu May, yongeyeho ati "Ba Minisitiri b'Intebe bakomeza imirimo yabo iyo bashyize mu bikorwa amasezerano yabo".
Bwana Farage yavuze ko ari ngombwa ko abanyapolitiki bumva ko badakwiriye kuba mu gihe bashaka guhungabanya icyemezo cyafashwe muri Referendum yo mu 2016.
Yagize ati "Ubu ni ikibazo cy'icyizere hagati yacu, abaturage, n'abatuye mu nzego za politiki".
Bagerageza guhirika Brexit kandi turi hano kugira ngo tubabwire ko tutabareka ngo bagende.
Mu butumwa yagejeje ku mbaga y'abantu bari bishimye, yongeyeho ati: "Ndashaka ko mwatuma abanyapolitiki bacu, bari hafi gutenguha icyemezo cya Brexit, bumva batisanzuye.
"Turimo turashyira mu bikorwa ingabo z'abaturage b'iki gihugu cyaduhaye intsinzi muri Brexit kandi ntikizaruhuka kugeza igihe tuzaba turi ubwongereza bw'ishema, bwigenga kandi bwigenga".
Hagati aho, abashyigikiye kuguma muri EU bakoze urugendo banyuze mu mujyi wa Birmingham mbere yo gukora imyigaragambyo y'amasaha abiri mu mujyi rwagati.
Bamwe mu banyamuryango b'ishyaka rya Tories Against Brexit bashyize ku karubanda amafoto y'ishyaka rya Tories Against Brexit nyuma y'uko iryo shyaka rishinzwe mu mpera z'icyumweru gishize.
Umukozi w'ishyaka Lord Adonis yasetse abadepite b'abashoramari kubera ibibazo by'umutekano bagize muri porogaramu y'ishyaka mu ntangiriro y'inama.
"Aba ni abantu batubwira ko bashobora kugira Iterambere ry'ikoranabuhanga rya Kanada, kugira umupaka udafite amakimbirane, kwishimira isoko ry'ubuntu ritagira umupaka muri Ireland".
