Ikinyamakuru Boston Globe cyatangaje ko uyu mugore w'umudemokarate wa Massachusetts yavuze ku bijyanye n'imibereho ye y'igihe kizaza ku wa gatandatu mu nama yabereye mu mujyi wo mu burengerazuba bwa Massachusetts.
Warren, unenga cyane Perezida Donald Trump, azitegura kongera kwiyamamaza mu Gushyingo ashyamiranye na Geoff Diehl w'Umurepublika, wabaye umuyobozi wungirije w'ibikorwa bya Trump muri 2016 muri Massachusetts.
