Icyiciro cya mbere: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer yatsinze ibitego bibiri bya Giants ku kibuga cya Dundee
Dundee Stars yongeye gutsindwa ku wa Gatanu muri Elite League na Belfast Giants batsinze umukino wo kwishyura 5-3 i Dundee ku wa Gatandatu.
Ikipe ya Giants yabonye igitego cya mbere cyatsinzwe n'ibitego bibiri bya Patrick Dwyer na Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan na Jordan Cownie bahuye ku busa bwa mbere mbere y'uko Dwyer ashyiraho igitego cya Giants.
Francois Bouchard yasinye igitego kimwe kuri Dundee mbere y'uko ibitego bibiri bya Lukas Lundvald Nielsen bibaha amahirwe yo gutsinda.
Ni igitego cya gatatu cya shampiyona cy'uyu mwaka cy'abakinnyi ba Adam Keefe, batsinze Dundee 2-1 mu kibuga cy'i Belfast ku wa Gatanu.
Ni umukino wa kane w'iyi shampiyona hagati y'amakipe yombi, aho iyi kipe yatsinze imikino itatu yaherukaga.
Igitego cya mbere cya Dwyer cyaje ku munota wa 3:35 ku mupira w'umuteresi wa Kendall McFaull, naho icya kabiri kiza iminota ine nyuma y'aho ku ruhande rwa Beauvillier nyuma y'umupira w'umuteresi wa David Rutherford.
Mu gihe cy'imyidagaduro, Sullivan yongeye gushyira ikipe y'iwabo mu mukino saa 13:10 mbere yuko Matt Marquardt yafashaga Cownie gutsinda igitego cya mbere cy'iminota 15:16.
Dwyer yemeye ko Giants yajya imbere mu ijonjora mbere y'ikiruhuko cya mbere ubwo yatsindaga igitego cya kabiri ku mugoroba ku mpera y'igice cya mbere.
Ikipe y'iwabo yongeye guhura maze Bouchard yongera gutsinda igitego cy'umukino wo kwishyura ku munota wa 27:37.
Cownie na Charles Corcoran bafatanyije kugira ngo bafashe Nielsen gutsinda Dundee ku nshuro ya mbere mu mukino ku mpera y'igice cya kabiri, maze atsinda igitego cya gatanu cyatsinzwe n'ikipe ye mu gice cya kabiri cy'igice cya nyuma.
Giants, ubu yatsinzwe imikino ine muri itanu ishize, izakina umukino ukurikiyeho iwabo muri Milton Keynes, uzaba kuwa Gatanu.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe ingendo zo mu kirere yapfuye kugira ngo abantu babarirwa mu magana bari mu ndege batabawe n'umutingito
Umuyobozi w'ikigo gishinzwe indege muri Indoneziya, yahawe igihembo cy'indashyikirwa nyuma yo gupfa, kugira ngo indege yari itwaye abagenzi amagana, ihaguruke nta nkomyi.
Abantu barenga 800 bamaze gupfa ndetse n'abandi benshi baburiwe irengero nyuma y'umutingito ukomeye wibasiye ikirwa cya Sulawesi ku wa Gatanu w'iki cyumweru, utuma haba tsunami.
Imirasire y'umuriro ikomeje kwibasira ako gace ndetse n'abantu benshi baguye mu bihomoka by'umuyaga mu mujyi wa Palu.
Nubwo abo bakoranaga bahungaga kugira ngo barokore ubuzima bwabo, Anthonius Gunawan Agung, w'imyaka 21, yanze kuva ku kazi ke mu munara w'ibiro by'indege bya Mutiara Sis Al Jufri i Palu, wari uhuzagurika cyane.
