Umubare w'abasize Koreya y'Amajyaruguru wagabanutse mu gihe Kim ari ku butegetsi
Umubare w'abantu bahunze Koreya ya Ruguru bajya muri Koreya y'Epfo wagabanutse kuva Kim Jong Un yajya ku butegetsi mu myaka irindwi ishize, nk'uko byatangajwe n'umushyinga w'amategeko wa Koreya y'Epfo.
Park Byeong-seug, avuga ko Minisiteri y'ubumwe ya Koreya y'Epfo yavuze ko mu mwaka ushize, abantu 1.127 ari bo bahunze igihugu, naho mu mwaka wa 2011 bari 2.706.
Bwana Park yavuze ko ibipimo by'imipaka byagiye birushaho gukomera hagati ya Koreya ya Ruguru n'u Bushinwa ndetse n'ibiciro by'ingendo by'abantu banyura ku mupaka nabyo byari mu bintu by'ingenzi byateye iyo mpinduka.
Pyongyang ntacyo iravuga ku mugaragaro.
Abenshi mu batorokaga Koreya y'Amajyaruguru, amaherezo bahabwa ubwenegihugu bwa Koreya y'Epfo.
Seoul ivuga ko abanyakoreya barenga 30.000 bambutse umupaka mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko kuva intambara ya Koreya yarangira mu 1953.
Benshi bahungira mu Bushinwa, igihugu gifite umupaka munini uhuza Koreya ya ruguru, kandi byoroshye kuwucamo kurusha agace kagenzurwa cyane hagati ya Koreya zombi.
Ubushinwa bufata abahunze nk'abimukira mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko aho kuba impunzi, kandi akenshi babaha uburenganzira bwo gusubira mu gihugu cyabo.
Imibanire hagati y'amajyaruguru n'amajyepfo (mu by'ukuri ikomeje kuba mu ntambara) yazamutse cyane mu mezi ashize.
Muri uku kwezi, abakuru b'ibihugu byombi bahuriye i Pyongyang mu biganiro byibanze ku biganiro byo kurandura intwaro za kirimbuzi zari zihagaze.
Ibi byabaye nyuma y'inama y'amateka yahuje Perezida wa Amerika Donald Trump na Kim Jong-un mu kwezi kwa gatandatu mu gihugu cya Singapore, aho byemeranyijwe ko bagiye gukora kugira ngo bakureho intwaro kirimbuzi ku nkengero ya Koreya.
Ariko ku wa gatandatu, minisitiri w'ububanyi n'amahanga wa Koreya ya ruguru, Ri Yong-ho, yavuze ko ibihano bya Amerika ari byo byatumye nta terambere rigaragara kuva icyo gihe.
"Niba tudashobora kwiringira Amerika, ntabwo dushobora kwiringira umutekano wacu w'igihugu, kandi, muri ibyo bihe, nta bushobozi na bumwe buhari bwo kwiyambura intwaro ku ruhande rumwe mbere", Bwana Ri yatangaje mu ijambo yavugiye imbere y'Inteko Rusange y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye i New York.
Nancy Pelosi yavuze ko Brett Kavanaugh ari "indyarya" kandi ko adakwiriye kuba mu Rukiko rw'Ikirenga
Umuyobozi w'abadepite mu Nteko ishinga amategeko, Nancy Pelosi, yise umukandida mu Rukiko rw'Ikirenga Brett Kavanaugh "umuherwe" kandi avuga ko atari agikwiriye mu by'umuco kuba mu Rukiko rw'Ikirenga.
Pelosi yavuze aya magambo mu kiganiro cyabaye ku wa gatandatu mu birori by'umunsi mukuru wa Texas Tribune Festival i Austin, Texas.
"Sinabashije kwiyumvisha ko umugore yakwifata muri ubwo buryo, nzamwita indaya", Pelosi yavuze kubijyanye n'uburyo yitabiriye amagambo ya Kavanaugh imbere y'akanama nkemurampaka ka sena ku wa kane.
Kavanaugh yahakanye ku buryo bugaragara ibirego byo gusambanya Dr. Christine Blasey Ford igihe bari ingimbi.
Mu ijambo rye rya mbere, Kavanaugh yagaragaje ko yari afite akanyamuneza, rimwe na rimwe agera ubwo ararira cyane ndetse akagira n'icyo avuga igihe yavugaga umuryango we n'imyaka ye yo mu mashuri yisumbuye.
Yamaganiye ku mugaragaro abademokarate bari muri iyo komite, avuga ko ibirego byamuregaga ari "ubwicanyi budafite ishingiro kandi buhuriweho" bwateguwe n'aba-liberali barakajwe n'uko Hillary Clinton yatsinzwe mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu yo mu 2016.
Pelosi yavuze ko yemera ko ibyo Kavanaugh yavuze byerekana ko atagomba kujya mu rukiko rw'ikirenga kuko byerekana ko afite urwikekwe ku bademocrate.
Yagize ati "Ntekereza ko yiyamiriza ubwe muri aya magambo ye n'uburyo yarwanyije Clinton n'abademokarate".
Pelosi yarabihakanye ubwo yabazwaga niba azagerageza guhangana na Kavanaugh aramutse yemejwe ku butegetsi kandi Abademokarate bagatsinda cyane mu Nteko Ishinga Amategeko.
"Icyo navuga ni iki: niba utari kubwiza ukuri Kongere cyangwa FBI, ubwo ntabwo ukwiye kuba mu Rukiko rw'Ikirenga gusa, ahubwo no mu rukiko uriho ubu", Pelosi yagize icyo avuga.
Kavanaugh ubu ni umucamanza mu rukiko rw'ubujurire rw'intara ya Washington DC.
