Ni gute intambara y'ubucuruzi hagati ya Amerika n'Ubushinwa ishobora kuba ingirakamaro kuri Beijing
Ibibazo by'intambara y'ubucuruzi hagati ya Amerika n'Ubushinwa byatangiye bikananirwa, kandi nubwo intambara ikiri ndende, kuba ibihugu byombi byaravuye mu mishyikirano bishobora kuba ingirakamaro kuri Beijing mu gihe kirekire, nkuko byemezwa n'impuguke.
Perezida Donald Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, yatanze umuburo wa mbere mu ntangiriro z'uyu mwaka, avuga ko ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi by'u Bushinwa byoherezwa mu mahanga harimo imirasire y'izuba, ibyuma na aluminiyumu.
Icya mbere gikomeye cyabaye muri iki cyumweru ubwo hashyirwagaho imisoro mishya igera kuri miliyari 200 z'amadolari, y'ibicuruzwa biva mu Bushinwa byinjira muri Amerika.
Buri gihe Beijing yagiye irwanaho mu buryo bumwe, mu buryo buherutse kuzamura ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa bya Amerika bifite agaciro ka miriyari 60 z'amadolari, bikava kuri 5 kugeza kuri 10 ku ijana.
Ubushinwa bwavuze ko buzakurikiza urugero rwa Amerika, kandi bisa n'aho ubukungu bwa kabiri ku isi budashobora guhinduka mu gihe gito.
Kugira ngo Washington yisubireho, bizasaba ko yitaba ibyo ishaka, ariko kwitaba Amerika ku mugaragaro, bizatera isoni Perezida w'Ubushinwa, Xi Jinping.
Nyamara, impuguke zivuga ko niba Beijing izi gukina neza, ibigeragezo by'intambara y'ubucuruzi na Amerika bishobora kugirira akamaro u Bushinwa mu gihe kirekire mu kugabanya ubwikorezi bw'ubukungu bw'ibihugu byombi.
"Kuko politiki yihuse ya Washington cyangwa Beijing ishobora gutuma habaho ibihe by'ibibazo by'ubukungu mu bihugu byombi, birakabije kuba bibi kurusha uko byavuzwe mbere", niko Abigail Grace, umushakashatsi wo muri Aziya w'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'umutekano muri Amerika, yavuze.
Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga wa Siriya ati "Siriya yiteguye kwakira impunzi"
Syria ivuga ko yiteguye kwakira impunzi z'impunzi ku bushake kandi ko isaba inkunga mu bikorwa byo kubaka igihugu cyayogojwe n'intambara imaze imyaka irenga irindwi.
Mu ijambo yavugiye mu Nteko rusange y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga, Walid al-Moualem, yavuze ko ibintu birimo kugenda neza.
Yagize ati "Uyu munsi ibintu biragenda neza kandi umutekano uragenda wiyongera bitewe n'uko hari intambwe duteye mu kurwanya iterabwoba".
Guverinoma ikomeje gusana ibigo byangijwe n'iterabwoba kugira ngo ibintu byongere kuba nk'uko byari bisanzwe.
Ubu noneho, ibintu byose byasabwe birimo gukorwa kugira ngo impunzi zisubire mu gihugu ku bushake bwazo, z'abantu bavuye mu bihugu by'amahanga kubera iterabwoba n'ingamba z'ubukungu z'amaboko y'igihemu zabangamiye imibereho yabo ya buri munsi n'imibereho yabo.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye ugereranya ko abaturage barenga miliyoni 5.5 bo muri Siriya bahunze igihugu kuva intambara itangira mu 2011.
Abandi bantu bagera kuri miliyoni esheshatu bakomeje kuba muri icyo gihugu kandi bakeneye ubufasha bw'ubutabazi.
Al-Moualem yavuze ko ubutegetsi bwa Syria bwishimira ubufasha bwose bwahabwa mu kubaka igihugu cyasenyutse.
Ariko kandi, yavuze ko atazemera gufashwa n'ibihugu bishyigikiye iyo myigaragambyo.
U Burayi bwatsinze mu mikino ya Ryder Cup i Paris
Ikipe y'i Burayi yatwaye igikombe cya Ryder Cup 2018 itsinze ikipe y'Amerika ku manota 16,5 ku 10,5 ku mukino wa nyuma wabereye mu kigo cy'umupira w'amaguru cya Le Golf National kiri hanze y'umujyi wa Paris mu Bufaransa.
Ni itsindwa rya gatandatu rikurikiranya ry'Amerika ku butaka bw'i Burayi kandi ntiriba ryaratsinze igikombe cya Ryder mu Burayi kuva mu 1993.
Uburayi bwasubije igikombe igihe ikipe ya kapiteni w'ikipe ya Denmark Thomas Bjorn yageraga ku manota 14.5 bari bakeneye kugira ngo batsinde Amerika.
Umunyamerika Phil Mickelson, wari waratsinze cyane muri iri rushanwa, yajugunye umupira mu mazi ku isahani ya 16 y'impar 3 atakaza umukino we kuri Francesco Molinari.
Umunya-Golf w'Umutaliyani yaraye agaragara mu mikino ye yose, aba umwe mu bakinnyi bane gusa bageze ku gitego 5-0-0 kuva ubwo hatangizwaga uburyo bw'irushanwa muri 1979.
