Amakuru y'umwuzure utukura: Umubare w'ibice by'umuyaga uri kugabanuka muri Pinellas, Manatee na Sarasota
Raporo ya vuba y'ikigo gishinzwe kurinda inyamaswa no kurinda amafi muri leta ya Florida, ivuga ko mu bice bimwe by'ikigobe cya Tampa, ubwiyongere bw'amazi atukura bwagiye bugabanuka.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'iri shyirahamwe, hari ibyerekeye ubutaka bw'ibiti by'imyelayo bigenda birushaho kuba bibi mu turere twa Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte no mu turere twa Collier, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko ubutaka bwuzura.
Umusozi wa Red Tide ufite uburebure bwa kirometero 210 uvuye ku nkombe y'inyanja uvuye mu majyaruguru ya Pinellas ukagera mu majyepfo ya Lee.
Imirwano ishobora kuba ibera mu birometero 16 uvuye ku nkombe z'ikiyaga cya Hillsborough, ariko ahantu hatoya ugereranyije n'aho yari iri mu cyumweru gishize.
Nanone kandi, mu ntara ya Pasco habaye umwuzure utukura.
Mu cyumweru gishize, twabonye ibipimo by'ubucucike bwo hagati mu nyanja no mu nkengero z'inkombe za leta ya Pinellas, ibipimo by'ubucucike bwo hasi no mu nkombe z'inyanja kure y'inkombe za leta ya Hillsborough, ibipimo by'ubucucike bwo hasi no mu nkombe z'inyanja kure y'inkombe za leta ya Sarasota, ibipimo by'ubucucike bwo hagati mu nkombe z'inyanja no mu nkombe z'intara ya Charlotte, ibipimo by'ubucucike bwo hasi no mu nkombe z'inyanja kure y'inkombe z'inyanja za leta ya Lee, n'ibipimo by'ubucucike bwo hasi no mu nkombe z'inyanja kure y'inkombe z'inyanja ya leta ya Collier.
Mu turere twa Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee na Collier, hakomeje kugaragara ko abantu bafite ibibazo by'ubuhumekero.
Nta murwayi w'ubwoko nk'ubu wari umaze icyumweru avugwa mu majyaruguru y'uburengerazuba bwa Florida.
